49 template<unsigned int spacedim>
50 class OmegaFluxDissipation00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
51 {
52 
53 private:
54 
58  const double D;
59 
60 public:
61 
79  OmegaFluxDissipation00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
80  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
81  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
82  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
83  const double D,
84  const unsigned int method,
85  const double alpha = 0.0)
86  :
87  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 3, 0, 0, 1, method, alpha, "OmegaFluxDissipation00"),
88  D(D)
89  {
90  }
91 
95  bool
96  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
97  const double /*t*/,
98  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
99  double& omega,
100  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
101  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
102  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
103  const bool compute_dq)
104  const
105  {
106  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> i;
107  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
108  i[m] = values[m];
109  const double q = values[3] > 1e-16 ? values[3] : 1e-16;
110 
111  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
112  {
113  omega = 1.0 / ( 2.0 * D * q) * i * i;
114  }
115 
116  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
117  {
118  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
119  d_omega[m] = 1.0 / ( D * q ) * i[m];
120  }
121 
122  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
123  {
124  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
125  d2_omega(m, m) = 1.0 / ( D * q );
126 
127  if(compute_dq && (q > 1e-16))
128  {
129  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
130  d2_omega(m, 3) = - 1.0 / ( D * q * q ) * i[m];
131  }
132  }
133 
134  return false;
135  }
136 
137 };

156 template<unsigned int spacedim>
157 class OmegaDualFluxDissipation00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
158 {
159 
160 private:
161 
165  const double D;
166 
167 public:
168 
186  OmegaDualFluxDissipation00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
187  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
188  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
189  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
190  const double D,
191  const unsigned int method,
192  const double alpha = 0.0)
193  :
194  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 0, 3, 1, method, alpha, "OmegaDualFluxDissipation00"),
195  D(D)
196  {
197  }
198 
202  bool
203  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
204  const double /*t*/,
205  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
206  double& omega,
207  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
208  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
209  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
210  const bool compute_dq)
211  const
212  {
213  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> E;
214  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
215  E[m] = values[m];
216  const double q = values[3];
217 
218  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
219  {
220  omega = -D * q / 2.0 * E * E;
221  }
222 
223  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
224  {
225  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
226  d_omega[m] = -D * q * E[m];
227  }
228 
229  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
230  {
231  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
232  d2_omega(m, m) = -D * q;
233 
234  if(compute_dq)
235  {
236  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
237  d2_omega(m, 3) = -D * E[m];
238  }
239  }
240 
241 
242  return false;
243  }
244 
245 };

257 template<unsigned int spacedim>
258 class OmegaMixedTerm00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
259 {
260 
261 public:
262 
278  OmegaMixedTerm00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
279  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
280  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
281  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
282  const unsigned int method,
283  const double alpha = 0.0)
284  :
285  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 1, 1, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaMixedTerm00")
286  {
287  }
288 
292  bool
293  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
294  const double /*t*/,
295  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
296  double& omega,
297  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
298  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
299  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
300  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
301  const
302  {
303  const double c_dot = values[0];
304  const double eta = values[1];
305 
306  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
307  {
308  omega = -c_dot * eta;
309  }
310 
311  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
312  {
313  d_omega[0] = -eta;
314  d_omega[1] = -c_dot;
315  }
316 
317  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
318  {
319  d2_omega(0, 0) = d2_omega(1, 1) = 0.0;
320  d2_omega(0, 1) = d2_omega(1, 0) = -1.0;
321  }
322 
323  return false;
324  }
325

342 template<unsigned int spacedim>
343 class OmegaMixedTerm01 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
344 {
345 
346 public:
347 
363  OmegaMixedTerm01( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
364  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
365  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
366  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
367  const unsigned int method,
368  const double alpha = 0.0)
369  :
370  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 3, 3, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaMixedTerm01")
371  {
372  }
373 
377  bool
378  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
379  const double /*t*/,
380  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
381  double& omega,
382  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
383  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
384  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
385  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
386  const
387  {
388  const double D_x = values[0];
389  const double D_y = values[1];
390  const double D_z = values[2];
391  const double E_x = values[3];
392  const double E_y = values[4];
393  const double E_z = values[5];
394 
395  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
396  {
397  omega = - D_x * E_x - D_y * E_y - D_z * E_z;
398  }
399 
400  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
401  {
402  d_omega[0] = -E_x;
403  d_omega[1] = -E_y;
404  d_omega[2] = -E_z;
405  d_omega[3] = -D_x;
406  d_omega[4] = -D_y;
407  d_omega[5] = -D_z;
408  }
409 
410  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
411  {
412  d2_omega(0, 3) = d2_omega(3, 0) = -1.0;
413  d2_omega(1, 4) = d2_omega(4, 1) = -1.0;
414  d2_omega(2, 5) = d2_omega(5, 2) = -1.0;
415  }
416 
417  return false;
418  }

517 template<unsigned int spacedim>
518 class OmegaDivergenceConstraint00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
519 {
520 
521 public:
522 
538  OmegaDivergenceConstraint00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
539  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
540  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
541  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
542  const unsigned int method,
543  const double alpha = 0.0)
544  :
545  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 1, 1, 1, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaDivergenceConstraint00")
546  {
547  }
548 
552  bool
553  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
554  const double /*t*/,
555  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
556  double& omega,
557  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
558  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
559  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
560  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
561  const
562  {
563  const double div_I_dot = values[0];
564  const double c_dot = values[1];
565  const double mu = values[2];
566 
567 
568  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
569  {
570  omega = -mu * (div_I_dot + c_dot);
571  }
572 
573  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
574  {
575  d_omega[0] = -mu;
576  d_omega[1] = -mu;
577  d_omega[2] = -(div_I_dot + c_dot);
578  }
579 
580  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
581  {
582  d2_omega(0, 2) = d2_omega(2, 0) = -1.0;
583  d2_omega(1, 2) = d2_omega(2, 1) = -1.0;
584  }
585 
586  return false;
587  }
588

605 template<unsigned int spacedim>
606 class OmegaZeroNormalFlux00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
607 {
608 
609 public:
610 
626  OmegaZeroNormalFlux00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
627  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
628  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
629  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
630  const unsigned int method,
631  const double alpha = 0.0)
632  :
633  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 3, 0, 1, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaZeroNormalFlux00")
634  {
635  }
636 
640  bool
641  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
642  const double /*t*/,
643  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
644  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
645  double& sigma,
646  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
647  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
648  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
649  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
650  const
651  {
652  const double I_x_dot = values[0];
653  const double I_y_dot = values[1];
654  const double I_z_dot = values[2];
655  const double mu = values[3];
656  const double n_x = n[0];
657  const double n_y = n[1];
658  const double n_z = spacedim==3 ? n[2] : 0.0;
659 
660  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
661  {
662  sigma = -mu * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z);
663  }
664 
665  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
666  {
667  d_sigma[0] = -mu * n_x;
668  d_sigma[1] = -mu * n_y;
669  d_sigma[2] = -mu * n_z;
670  d_sigma[3] = -(I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z);
671  }
672 
673  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
674  {
675  d2_sigma(0, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 0) = -n_x;
676  d2_sigma(1, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 1) = -n_y;
677  d2_sigma(2, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 2) = -n_z;
678  }
679 
680  return false;
681  }
682 
683 };

697 template<unsigned int spacedim>
698 class OmegaFluxPower00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
699 {
700 private:
701 
705  dealii::Function<spacedim>&
706  function_mu;
707 
708 public:
709 
727  OmegaFluxPower00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
728  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
729  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
730  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
731  dealii::Function<spacedim>& function_mu,
732  const unsigned int method,
733  const double alpha = 0.0)
734  :
735  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 3, 0, 0, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaFluxPower00"),
736  function_mu(function_mu)
737  {
738  }
739 
743  bool
744  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
745  const double t,
746  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& x,
747  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
748  double& sigma,
749  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
750  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& /*d2_sigma*/,
751  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
752  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
753  const
754  {
755  const double time_old = function_mu.get_time();
756  function_mu.set_time(t);
757  const double mu_bar = function_mu.value(x);
758  function_mu.set_time(time_old);
759 
760  const double I_x_dot = values[0];
761  const double I_y_dot = values[1];
762  const double I_z_dot = values[2];
763  const double n_x = n[0];
764  const double n_y = n[1];
765  const double n_z = spacedim==3 ? n[2] : 0.0;
766 
767  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
768  {
769  sigma = mu_bar * (I_x_dot * n_x + I_y_dot * n_y + I_z_dot * n_z);
770  }
771 
772  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
773  {
774  d_sigma[0] = mu_bar * n_x;
775  d_sigma[1] = mu_bar * n_y;
776  d_sigma[2] = mu_bar * n_z;
777  }
778 
779  return false;
780  }
781 
782 };

922  OmegaDualFluxPower00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
923  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,

931  function_i(function_i)

938  bool
939  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,

956 
957  const double eta = values[0];
958 
959  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))

1034  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& /*n*/,
1035  double& sigma,
1036  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
1037  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& /*d2_sigma*/,
1038  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
1039  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
1040  const
1041  {
1042 
1043  const double time_old = function_f.get_time();
1044  function_f.set_time(t);
1045  const double f_x = function_f.value(x, 0);
1046  const double f_y = function_f.value(x, 1);
1047  const double f_z = function_f.value(x, 2);
1048  function_f.set_time(time_old);
1049 
1050  const double u_x_dot = values[0];
1051  const double u_y_dot = values[1];
1052  const double u_z_dot = values[2];
1053 
1054  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
1055  {
1056  sigma = - (f_x * u_x_dot + f_y * u_y_dot + f_z * u_z_dot);
1057  }
1058 
1059  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
1060  {
1061  d_sigma[0] = -f_x;
1062  d_sigma[1] = -f_y;
1063  d_sigma[2] = -f_z;
1064  }
1065 
1066  return false;
1067  }
1068

1113  OmegaInterfaceFluxDissipation00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,

1152  }

1159  }

1167  d2_sigma(1,1) = 1.0/D * n_y * n_y;

1189 template<unsigned int spacedim>
1190 class OmegaDualButlerVolmer00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
1191 {
1192 private:
1193 
1197  const double
1198  I_0;
1199 
1203  const double
1204  beta;
1205 
1209  const double
1210  RT;
1211 
1216  const double
1217  threshold;
1218 
1219 public:
1220 
1244  OmegaDualButlerVolmer00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
1245  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
1246  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
1247  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
1248  const double I_0,
1249  const double beta,
1250  const double RT,
1251  const double threshold,
1252  const unsigned int method,
1253  const double alpha = 0.0)
1254  :
1255  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 0, 1, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaDualButlerVolmer00"),
1256  I_0(I_0),
1257  beta(beta),
1258  RT(RT),
1259  threshold(threshold)
1260  {
1261  }
1262 
1266  bool
1267  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
1268  const double /*t*/,
1269  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
1270  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& /*n*/,
1271  double& sigma,
1272  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
1273  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
1274  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
1275  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
1276  const
1277  {
1278 
1279  const double eta = values[0];
1280 
1281  double t1, t2;
1282 
1283  if(eta / RT > threshold)
1284  {
1285  t1 = exp(beta * threshold);
1286  t2 = exp( (beta - 1.0) * threshold);
1287  }
1288  else if(eta / RT < -threshold)
1289  {
1290  t1 = exp(-beta * threshold);
1291  t2 = exp( -(beta - 1.0) * threshold);
1292  }
1293  else
1294  {
1295  t1 = exp(beta * eta / RT);
1296  t2 = exp( (beta - 1.0) * eta / RT);
1297  }
1298 
1299  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
1300  {
1301  if(eta / RT > threshold)
1302  sigma = t1 / beta + t2 / (1.0 - beta) + (t1 - t2) * (eta / RT - threshold) + 0.5 * (beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2) * (eta / RT - threshold) * (eta / RT - threshold);
1303  else if(eta / RT < -threshold)
1304  sigma = t1 / beta + t2 / (1.0 - beta) + (t1 - t2) * (eta / RT + threshold) + 0.5 * (beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2) * (eta / RT + threshold) * (eta / RT + threshold);
1305  else
1306  sigma = t1/beta + t2/(1.0 - beta);
1307  sigma *= -I_0;
1308  }
1309 
1310  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
1311  {
1312  if(eta / RT > threshold)
1313  {
1314  d_sigma[0] = (t1 - t2) + (beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2) * (eta / RT - threshold);
1315  }
1316  else if(eta / RT < -threshold)
1317  {
1318  d_sigma[0] = (t1 - t2) + (beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2) * (eta / RT + threshold);
1319  }
1320  else
1321  {
1322  d_sigma[0] = (t1 - t2);
1323  }
1324  d_sigma[0] *= -I_0 / RT;
1325  }
1326 
1327  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
1328  {
1329  if(eta / RT > threshold)
1330  {
1331  d2_sigma(0,0) = beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2;
1332  }
1333  else if(eta / RT < -threshold)
1334  {
1335  d2_sigma(0,0) = beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2;
1336  }
1337  else
1338  {
1339  d2_sigma(0,0) = beta * t1 + (1.0 - beta) * t2;
1340  }
1341  d2_sigma(0,0) *= -I_0 / RT / RT;
1342  }
1343 
1344  return false;
1345  }
1346 
1347 };

1454  }

1458  {

1460  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1461  {
1462  d2_sigma(m, m+6) = d2_sigma(m+6, m) = 1.0;
1463  if(!u_1_as_parameter)
1464  d2_sigma(m+3, m+6) = -1.0;
1465  d2_sigma(m+6, m+3) = -1.0;
1466  }
1467  }
1468

1470  }

1509 template<unsigned int spacedim>
1510 class OmegaDualIonDissipation00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
1511 {
1512 
1513 private:
1514 
1518  const double
1519  D;
1520 
1524  const double
1525  V_m_f;
1526 
1527 
1528 public:
1529 
1549  OmegaDualIonDissipation00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
1550  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
1551  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
1552  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
1553  const double D,
1554  const double V_m_f,
1555  const unsigned int method,
1556  const double alpha = 0.0)
1557  :
1558  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 1, 0, 4, 11, method, alpha, "OmegaDualIonDissipation00"),
1559  D(D),
1560  V_m_f(V_m_f)
1561  {
1562  }
1563 
1567  bool
1568  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
1569  const double /*t*/,
1570  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
1571  double& omega,
1572  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
1573  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
1574  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
1575  const bool compute_dq)
1576  const
1577  {
1578 
1579  const double c_dot = values[0];
1580  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_eta;
1581  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1582  grad_eta[m] = values[m+1];
1583  const double eta = values[4];
1584  const double c = values[5];
1585  const double c_f = values[6];
1586  dealii::Tensor<2, 3> F, C, C_inv;
1587  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1588  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
1589  F[m][n] = values[7 + m * 3 + n];
1590  C = transpose(F) * F;
1591  C_inv = invert(C);
1592  const double J = determinant(F);
1593  const double n_f = c_f / J * V_m_f;
1594  const dealii::Tensor<1, 3> A = C_inv * grad_eta;
1595  const double grad_eta_C_inv_grad_eta = A * grad_eta;
1596 
1597  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
1598  {
1599  omega = -0.5 * D * c / n_f * grad_eta_C_inv_grad_eta - eta * c_dot;
1600  }
1601 
1602  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
1603  {
1604  d_omega[0] = -eta;
1605  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1606  d_omega[m + 1] = -D * c / n_f * A[m];
1607  d_omega[4] = -c_dot;
1608  }
1609 
1610  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
1611  {
1612  d2_omega = 0.0;
1613  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1614  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
1615  d2_omega(m + 1, n + 1) = -D * c / n_f * C_inv[m][n];
1616  d2_omega(0, 4) = d2_omega(4, 0) = -1.0;
1617 
1618  if(compute_dq)
1619  {
1620  const dealii::Tensor<1,3> F_A = F * A;
1621  const dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_C_inv = F * C_inv;
1622  dealii::Vector<double> F_vect(9), dJ_dF(9);
1623  for(unsigned i = 0; i < 9; ++i)
1624  F_vect[i] = values[7 + i];
1625  get_dJ_dF(F_vect, dJ_dF);
1626 
1627  for(unsigned int L = 0; L < 3; ++L)
1628  {
1629  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1630  for(unsigned int M = 0; M < 3; ++M)
1631  d2_omega[1 + L][7 + m * 3 + M] = (- D / V_m_f * A[L] * dJ_dF[m * 3 + M] + D * J / V_m_f * (C_inv[L][M] * F_A[m] + A[M] * F_C_inv[m][L] ) ) * c / c_f;
1632  d2_omega[1 + L][5] = - D * J / V_m_f * 1.0 / c_f * A[L];
1633  d2_omega[1 + L][6] = D * J / V_m_f * c / c_f / c_f * A[L];
1634  }
1635  }
1636 
1637 
1638  }
1639 
1640  return false;
1641 
1642  }
1643 
1644 };

1914  {

1916  const unsigned int i_c_f_dot = 0;
1917  const unsigned int i_grad_eta_f = 1;
1918  vector<unsigned int> i_grad_eta_i(I);
1919  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1920  i_grad_eta_i[i] = 4 + 3*i;

1929  const double c_f_dot = values[i_c_f_dot];
1930  const double c_f = values[i_c_f];
1931  dealii::Vector<double> c_i(I);
1932  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1933  c_i[i] = values[i_c_i[i]];
1934 
1935  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_eta, grad_eta_f;
1936  std::vector<dealii::Tensor<1,3>> grad_eta_i(I);
1937  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1938  {
1939  grad_eta[m] = values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
1940  grad_eta_f[m] = values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
1941  }
1942  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1943  {
1944  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1945  {
1946  grad_eta[m] += c_i[i]/c_f * values[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m];
1947  grad_eta_i[i][m] = values[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m];
1948  }
1949  }
1950 
1951  const double eta_f = values[i_eta_f];
1952 
1953  dealii::Tensor<2, 3> F, C, C_inv;
1954  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1955  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
1956  F[m][n] = values[i_F + m * 3 + n];
1957  C = transpose(F) * F;
1958  C_inv = invert(C);
1959  const dealii::Tensor<1, 3> C_inv_grad_eta = C_inv * grad_eta;
1960  const double grad_eta_C_inv_grad_eta = C_inv_grad_eta * grad_eta;
1961  const double J = determinant(F);
1962 
1963  const double K = D * J / V_m_f;
1964 
1965  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
1966  {
1967  omega = -0.5 * K * grad_eta_C_inv_grad_eta - eta_f * c_f_dot;
1968  }
1969 
1970  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
1971  {
1972  d_omega[i_c_f_dot] = -eta_f;
1973  d_omega[i_eta_f] = -c_f_dot;
1974  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1975  {
1976  d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] = -K * C_inv_grad_eta[m];
1977  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1978  d_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m] = d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] * c_i[i]/c_f;
1979  }
1980  }
1981 
1982  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
1983  {
1984  d2_omega = 0.0;
1985 
1986  d2_omega[i_c_f_dot][i_eta_f] = d2_omega[i_eta_f][i_c_f_dot] = -1.0;
1987 
1988  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
1989  {
1990  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
1991  {
1992  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m][i_grad_eta_f + n] = -K * C_inv[m][n];
1993  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
1994  {
1995  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m][i_grad_eta_i[i] + n] = d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + n][i_grad_eta_f + m] = -K * C_inv[m][n] * c_i[i]/c_f;
1996  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < I; ++j)
1997  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + n][i_grad_eta_i[j] + m] = -K * C_inv[m][n] * (c_i[i] / c_f) * (c_i[j] / c_f);
1998  }
1999  }
2000  }
2001 
2002  if(compute_dq)
2003  {
2004  const dealii::Tensor<1,3> A = C_inv * grad_eta;
2005  const dealii::Tensor<1,3> F_A = F * A;
2006  const dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_C_inv = F * C_inv;
2007  dealii::Vector<double> F_vect(9), dJ_dF(9);
2008  for(unsigned i = 0; i < 9; ++i)
2009  F_vect[i] = values[i_F + i];
2010  get_dJ_dF(F_vect, dJ_dF);
2011  dealii::Tensor<1,3> C_inv_sum_c_i_c_f_grad_eta_i;
2012  for(unsigned int L = 0; L < 3; ++L)
2013  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2014  C_inv_sum_c_i_c_f_grad_eta_i[L] += c_i[i]/c_f * grad_eta_i[i][L];
2015  C_inv_sum_c_i_c_f_grad_eta_i = C_inv * C_inv_sum_c_i_c_f_grad_eta_i;
2016 
2017  for(unsigned int L = 0; L < 3; ++L)
2018  {
2019  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2020  {
2021  for(unsigned int M = 0; M < 3; ++M)
2022  {
2023  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + L][i_F + m * 3 + M] = - D / V_m_f * A[L] * dJ_dF[m * 3 + M] + K * (C_inv[L][M] * F_A[m] + A[M] * F_C_inv[m][L] );
2024  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2025  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + L][i_F + m * 3 + M] = d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + L][i_F + m * 3 + M] * c_i[i] / c_f;
2026  }
2027  }
2028  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + L][i_c_f] = 1.0 / c_f * K * C_inv_sum_c_i_c_f_grad_eta_i[L];
2029  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2030  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + L][i_c_f] = K * (C_inv_sum_c_i_c_f_grad_eta_i[L] + A[L]) * c_i[i] / c_f / c_f;
2031  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < I; ++j)
2032  {
2033  const dealii::Tensor<1,3> C_inv_grad_eta_j = C_inv * grad_eta_i[j];
2034  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + L][i_c_i[j]] = -K * C_inv_grad_eta_j[L] / c_f;
2035  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2036  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + L][i_c_i[j]] = -K * C_inv_grad_eta_j[L] * c_i[i] / c_f / c_f;
2037  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[j] + L][i_c_i[j]] += -K * A[L] / c_f;
2038  }
2039  }
2040 
2041  }
2042  }
2043 
2044  return false;
2045 
2046  }
2047 
2048 };

2107  OmegaDualFluidDissipation01(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,

2140  vector<unsigned int> i_grad_eta_i(I);
2141  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2142  i_grad_eta_i[i] = 7 + 3*i;
2143  const unsigned int i_eta_f = 7 + 3*I;
2144  const unsigned int i_c_f = 8 + 3*I;
2145  vector<unsigned int> i_c_i(I);
2146  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2147  i_c_i[i] = 9 + 3*I + i;
2148 
2149  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_xi_dot;
2150  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2151  grad_xi_dot[m] = values[i_grad_xi_dot + m];
2152 
2153  const double c_f_dot = values[i_c_f_dot];
2154  const double c_f = values[i_c_f];
2155  dealii::Vector<double> c_i(I);
2156  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2157  c_i[i] = values[i_c_i[i]];
2158 
2159  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_eta;
2160  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2161  grad_eta[m] = values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
2162  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2163  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2164  grad_eta[m] += c_i[i]/c_f * values[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m];
2165

2167 
2168 
2169  const double eps = 0.0;
2170  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
2171  {
2172  omega = grad_xi_dot * grad_eta - eta_f * c_f_dot + grad_xi_dot * grad_xi_dot * 0.5 * eps;
2173  }
2174

2176  {
2177  d_omega[i_c_f_dot] = -eta_f;
2178  d_omega[i_eta_f] = -c_f_dot;

2180  {
2181  d_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m] = grad_eta[m];
2182  d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] = grad_xi_dot[m];
2183  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2184  d_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m] = grad_xi_dot[m] * c_i[i]/c_f;
2185  d_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m] += grad_xi_dot[m] * eps;
2186  }
2187  }
2188 
2189  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
2190  {
2191  d2_omega[i_c_f_dot][i_eta_f] = d2_omega[i_eta_f][i_c_f_dot] = -1.0;
2192 
2193  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2194  {
2195  d2_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m][i_grad_eta_f + m] = d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m][i_grad_xi_dot + m] = 1.0;
2196  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2197  d2_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m][i_grad_eta_i[i] + m] = d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m][i_grad_xi_dot + m] = c_i[i]/c_f;
2198  }
2199 
2200  if(compute_dq)
2201  {
2202  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2203  {
2204  d2_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m][i_c_f] = (values[i_grad_eta_f + m] - grad_eta[m]) / c_f;
2205  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2206  d2_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m][i_c_i[i]] = values[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m] / c_f;
2207  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2208  {
2209  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m][i_c_f] = -grad_xi_dot[m] * c_i[i]/c_f/c_f;
2210  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m][i_c_i[i]] = grad_xi_dot[m] * 1.0/c_f;
2211  }
2212  }
2213 
2214  }
2215 
2216  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2217  {
2218  d2_omega(i_grad_xi_dot + m, i_grad_xi_dot + m) += eps;
2219  }
2220 
2221  }
2222 
2223  return false;
2224 
2225  }

2317  OmegaDualFluidDissipation02(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
2318  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
2319  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
2320  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
2321  const unsigned int I,

2324  const double V_m_f,
2325  const unsigned int method,
2326  const double alpha = 0.0)
2327  :

2339  bool
2340  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
2341  const double /*t*/,
2342  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
2343  double& omega,
2344  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
2345  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
2346  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
2347  const bool compute_dq)
2348  const
2349  {
2350 
2351  (void)compute_dq;
2352  Assert(!compute_dq, dealii::ExcMessage("The alpha-family for temporal discretization is not currently implemented!"));
2353 
2354  // start indices for respective quantities
2355  const unsigned int i_F_dot = 0;
2356  const unsigned int i_grad_eta_f = 9;
2357  vector<unsigned int> i_grad_eta_i(I);
2358  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2359  i_grad_eta_i[i] = 12 + 3*i;
2360  const unsigned int i_eta_f = 12 + 3*I;
2361  vector<unsigned int> i_c_i(I);
2362  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2363  i_c_i[i] = 13 + 3*I + i;
2364  const unsigned int i_F = 13 + 4*I;
2365 
2366  dealii::Tensor<2, 3> F_dot, F;
2367  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2368  {
2369  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
2370  {
2371  F_dot[m][n] = values [i_F_dot + m * 3 + n];
2372  F[m][n] = values [i_F + m * 3 + n];
2373  }
2374  }
2375  dealii::Vector<double> c_i(I);
2376  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2377  c_i[i] = values[i_c_i[i]];
2378  const double J =determinant(F);
2379  const double c_f = (J - n_0) / V_m_f;
2380 
2381  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_eta;
2382  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2383  grad_eta[m] = values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
2384  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2385  {
2386  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2387  {
2388  grad_eta[m] += c_i[i]/c_f * values[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m];
2389  }
2390  }
2391 
2392  const double eta_f = values[i_eta_f];
2393 
2394  dealii::Tensor<2, 3> F_inv, C_inv;
2395  F_inv = invert(F);
2396  C_inv = F_inv * transpose(F_inv);
2397  const dealii::Tensor<1, 3> C_inv_grad_eta = C_inv * grad_eta;
2398  const double grad_eta_C_inv_grad_eta = C_inv_grad_eta * grad_eta;
2399 
2400  const double K = D * J / V_m_f;
2401 
2402  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
2403  {
2404  omega = -0.5 * K * grad_eta_C_inv_grad_eta - eta_f * J * scalar_product(F_inv, transpose(F_dot)) / V_m_f;
2405  }
2406 
2407  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
2408  {
2409  d_omega = 0.0;
2410  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2411  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
2412  d_omega[i_F_dot + m * 3 + n] = -eta_f * J / V_m_f * F_inv[n][m];
2413  d_omega[i_eta_f] = -J * scalar_product(F_inv, transpose(F_dot)) / V_m_f;
2414  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2415  {
2416  d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] = -K * C_inv_grad_eta[m];
2417  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2418  d_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m] = d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] * c_i[i]/c_f;
2419  }
2420  }
2421 
2422  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
2423  {
2424  d2_omega = 0.0;
2425  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2426  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
2427  d2_omega[i_F_dot + m * 3 + n][i_eta_f] = d2_omega[i_eta_f][i_F_dot + m * 3 + n] = -J / V_m_f * F_inv[n][m];
2428 
2429  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2430  {
2431  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
2432  {
2433  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m][i_grad_eta_f + n] = -K * C_inv[m][n];
2434  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2435  {
2436  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m][i_grad_eta_i[i] + n] = d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + n][i_grad_eta_f + m] = -K * C_inv[m][n] * c_i[i]/c_f;
2437  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < I; ++j)
2438  d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + n][i_grad_eta_i[j] + m] = -K * C_inv[m][n] * (c_i[i] / c_f) * (c_i[j] / c_f);
2439  }
2440  }
2441  }
2442  }
2443 
2444  return false;
2445 
2446  }

2612  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
2613  {
2614  omega = grad_xi_dot * grad_eta - eta_f * J * scalar_product(F_inv, transpose(F_dot)) / V_m_f;
2615  }
2616 
2617  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
2618  {
2619  d_omega = 0.0;
2620 
2621  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2622  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
2623  d_omega[i_F_dot + m * 3 + n] = -eta_f * J / V_m_f * F_inv[n][m];
2624  d_omega[i_eta_f] = -J * scalar_product(F_inv, transpose(F_dot)) / V_m_f;
2625  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2626  {
2627  d_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m] = grad_eta[m];
2628  d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] = grad_xi_dot[m];
2629  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2630  d_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m] = grad_xi_dot[m] * c_i[i]/c_f;
2631  }
2632  }
2633 
2634  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
2635  {
2636  d2_omega = 0.0;
2637  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2638  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
2639  d2_omega[i_F_dot + m * 3 + n][i_eta_f] = d2_omega[i_eta_f][i_F_dot + m * 3 + n] = -J / V_m_f * F_inv[n][m];
2640 
2641  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2642  {
2643  d2_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m][i_grad_eta_f + m] = d2_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m][i_grad_xi_dot + m] = 1.0;
2644  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2645  d2_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m][i_grad_eta_i[i] + m] = d2_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m][i_grad_xi_dot + m] = c_i[i]/c_f;
2646  }
2647  }
2648 
2649  return false;
2650 
2651  }
2652 };

2685 template<unsigned int spacedim>

2749  vector<unsigned int> i_grad_eta_i(I);

2751  i_grad_eta_i[i] = 10 + 3*i;
2752  const unsigned int i_eta_f = 10 + 3*I;
2753  const unsigned int i_c_f = 11 + 3*I;

2755  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2756  i_c_i[i] = 12 + 3*I + i;
2757  const unsigned int i_F = 11+ 4*I + 1;
2758 
2759  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_xi_dot;
2760  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2761  grad_xi_dot[m] = values[i_grad_xi_dot + m];
2762 
2763  const double c_f_dot = values[i_c_f_dot];
2764 
2765  dealii::Tensor<1,3> u_dot;
2766  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2767  u_dot[m] = values[i_u_dot + m];
2768 
2769  const double eta_f = values[i_eta_f];
2770 
2771  const double c_f = values[i_c_f];
2772  dealii::Vector<double> c_i(I);
2773  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2774  c_i[i] = values[i_c_i[i]];

2777  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2778  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)

2782  std::vector<dealii::Tensor<1,3>> grad_eta_i(I);
2783  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2784  {
2785  grad_eta_c_f[m] = c_f * values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
2786  grad_eta_f[m] = values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
2787  }

2789  {
2790  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2791  {
2792  grad_eta_c_f[m] += c_i[i] * values[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m];
2793  grad_eta_i[i][m] = values[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m];
2794  }
2795  }
2796 
2797  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv, C_inv;
2798  dealii::Tensor<1,3> C_inv_grad_xi_dot, grad_xi_dot_F_inv, I_dot_f_c_f, C_inv_grad_eta_c_f, grad_eta_c_f_F_inv, C_inv_grad_eta_f, F_inv_grad_eta_f, F_inv_u_dot;
2799  std::vector<dealii::Tensor<1,3>> C_inv_grad_eta_i(I), F_inv_grad_eta_i(I);
2800  F_inv = invert(F);
2801  C_inv = F_inv * transpose(F_inv);
2802  C_inv_grad_xi_dot = C_inv * grad_xi_dot;
2803  grad_xi_dot_F_inv = transpose(F_inv) * grad_xi_dot;
2804  I_dot_f_c_f = F_inv * (grad_xi_dot_F_inv - u_dot);
2805  C_inv_grad_eta_c_f = C_inv * grad_eta_c_f;
2806  grad_eta_c_f_F_inv = transpose(F_inv) * grad_eta_c_f;
2807  C_inv_grad_eta_f = C_inv * grad_eta_f;
2808  F_inv_grad_eta_f = transpose(F_inv) * grad_eta_f;
2809  F_inv_u_dot = F_inv * u_dot;

2811  {
2812  C_inv_grad_eta_i[i] = C_inv * grad_eta_i[i];
2813  F_inv_grad_eta_i[i] = transpose(F_inv) * grad_eta_i[i];
2814  }
2815 
2816  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
2817  {
2818  omega = I_dot_f_c_f * grad_eta_c_f - eta_f * c_f_dot;
2819  }
2820 
2821  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
2822  {
2823  d_omega[i_c_f_dot] = -eta_f;
2824  d_omega[i_eta_f] = -c_f_dot;
2825  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
2826  {
2827  d_omega[i_grad_xi_dot + m] = C_inv_grad_eta_c_f[m];
2828  d_omega[i_u_dot + m] = -grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[m];
2829  d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] = I_dot_f_c_f [m] * c_f;
2830  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2831  d_omega[i_grad_eta_i[i] + m] = I_dot_f_c_f[m] * c_i[i];
2832  }
2833  }
2834 
2835  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
2836  {
2837

2839

2841  {
2842  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
2843  {
2844  d2_omega(i_grad_xi_dot + m, i_grad_eta_f + n) = d2_omega(i_grad_eta_f + n, i_grad_xi_dot + m) = C_inv[m][n] * c_f;
2845  d2_omega(i_u_dot + m, i_grad_eta_f + n) = d2_omega(i_grad_eta_f + n, i_u_dot + m) = -F_inv[n][m] * c_f;
2846  }
2847  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2848  {

2852  d2_omega(i_u_dot + m, i_grad_eta_i[i] + n) = d2_omega(i_grad_eta_i[i] + n, i_u_dot + m) = -F_inv[n][m] * c_i[i];
2853  }

2864  d2_omega(i_u_dot + m, i_c_f) = -F_inv_grad_eta_f[m];

2870  d2_omega(i_grad_eta_i[i] + m, i_c_i[i]) = d_omega(i_grad_eta_i[i] + m) / c_i[i];
2871  }

2873  {

2877  d2_omega(i_u_dot + m, i_F + 3 * k + l) = grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[k] * F_inv[l][m];
2878  d2_omega(i_grad_eta_f + m, i_F + 3 * k + l) = (-C_inv_grad_xi_dot[l] * F_inv[m][k] - grad_xi_dot_F_inv[k] * C_inv[l][m] + F_inv_u_dot[l] * F_inv[m][k]) * c_f;
2879  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < I; ++i)
2880  d2_omega(i_grad_eta_i[i] + m, i_F + 3 * k + l) = (-C_inv_grad_xi_dot[l] * F_inv[m][k] - grad_xi_dot_F_inv[k] * C_inv[l][m] + F_inv_u_dot[l] * F_inv[m][k]) * c_i[i];
2881 
2882  }
2883  }
2884 
2885  }
2886 
2887  }
2888 
2889  }

2891  return false;

2893  }

3253  }
3254 
3258  bool
3259  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
3260  const double t,
3261  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& x,
3262  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& /*n*/,
3263  double& sigma,
3264  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
3265  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
3266  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
3267  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
3268  const
3269  {
3270 
3271  const double time_old = phi_bar.get_time();
3272  phi_bar.set_time(t);
3273  const double eta_bar_ = -A_e * F * phi_bar.value(x);
3274  phi_bar.set_time(time_old);
3275  const double eta_c = -A_e * F * phi_c;
3276 
3277  const double eta_int = values[0];
3278  const double delta_eta = eta_int + eta_bar_;
3279 
3280  if(A_e > 0)
3281  {
3282  const double delta_phi_ub_ = 1.0 / F / A_e * (eta_c - delta_eta);
3283  if(delta_phi_ub_ < delta_phi_ub)
3284  delta_phi_ub = delta_phi_ub_;
3285  }
3286  else
3287  {
3288  const double delta_phi_lb_ = 1.0 / F / A_e * (eta_c - delta_eta);
3289  if(delta_phi_lb_ > delta_phi_lb)
3290  delta_phi_lb = delta_phi_lb_;
3291  }
3292 
3293  if(delta_eta >= eta_c)
3294  electrolysis_active = true;
3295 
3296  if(is_active)
3297  {
3298  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
3299  {
3300  if(delta_eta >= eta_c)
3301  sigma = -1.0 / (2.0 * R) * (delta_eta - eta_c) * (delta_eta - eta_c);
3302  else
3303  sigma = 0.0;
3304  }
3305 
3306  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
3307  {
3308  if(delta_eta >= eta_c)
3309  d_sigma[0] = -1.0 / R * (delta_eta - eta_c);
3310  else
3311  d_sigma = 0.0;
3312  }
3313 
3314  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
3315  {
3316  if(delta_eta >= eta_c)
3317  d2_sigma[0][0] = -1.0 / R;
3318  else
3319  // small second derivative to ensure definiteness of system
3320  d2_sigma[0][0] = -regularization / R;
3321  }
3322  }
3323 
3324  return false;
3325  }
3326 
3327 };

3347 template<unsigned int spacedim>
3348 class OmegaElectrolysis01 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
3349 {
3350 private:
3351 
3355  const double
3356  F;
3357 
3361  const double
3362  RT;
3363 
3367  const double
3368  A_e;
3369 
3373  dealii::Function<spacedim>&
3374  phi_bar;
3375 
3379  const double
3380  i_0;
3381 
3385  const double
3386  R_el;
3387 
3388 public:
3389 
3418  OmegaElectrolysis01(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
3419  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
3420  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
3421  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
3422  const double F,
3423  const double RT,
3424  const double A_e,
3425  dealii::Function<spacedim>& phi_bar,
3426  const double i_0,
3427  const double R_el,
3428  const unsigned int method,
3429  const double alpha = 0.0)
3430  :
3431  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 0, 1, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaElectrolysis01"),
3432  F(F),
3433  RT(RT),
3434  A_e(A_e),
3435  phi_bar(phi_bar),
3436  i_0(i_0),
3437  R_el(R_el)
3438  {
3439  }
3440 
3444  bool
3445  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
3446  const double t,
3447  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& x,
3448  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& /*n*/,
3449  double& sigma,
3450  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
3451  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
3452  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
3453  const bool /*compute_dq*/)
3454  const
3455  {
3456 
3457  const double time_old = phi_bar.get_time();
3458  phi_bar.set_time(t);
3459  const double eta_bar_ = -A_e * F * phi_bar.value(x);
3460  phi_bar.set_time(time_old);
3461 
3462  const double eta_int = values[0];
3463  const double delta_eta = eta_int + eta_bar_;
3464 
3465  // iterate for corresponding current
3466  double I_k = 0.0;
3467  double f_old = 1e16;
3468  unsigned int iter = 0;
3469  for(;;)
3470  {
3471  iter++;
3472  const double f = asinh(I_k * F / i_0) + 1.0 / RT * R_el * F * F * I_k + delta_eta / RT;
3473  if(fabs(fabs(f) - fabs(f_old)) < 1e-16)
3474  break;
3475  if(iter == 100)
3476  return true;
3477  f_old = f;
3478  const double df_dI_k = (F / i_0) / sqrt( 1.0 + (I_k * F / i_0) * (I_k * F / i_0) ) + 1.0 / RT * R_el * F * F;
3479  const double dI_k = - f / df_dI_k;
3480  I_k = I_k + dI_k;
3481  }
3482 
3483  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
3484  sigma = delta_eta * I_k - i_0 * RT / F * ( sqrt( 1.0 + (I_k * F / i_0) * (I_k * F / i_0) ) - 1.0 ) + RT * I_k * asinh(I_k * F / i_0) + 0.5 * R_el * (I_k * F) * (I_k * F);
3485 
3486  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
3487  d_sigma[0] = I_k;
3488 
3489  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
3490  {
3491  d2_sigma[0][0] = -1.0 / (RT * F / i_0 / sqrt( 1.0 + (I_k * F / i_0) * (I_k * F / i_0) ) + R_el * F * F);
3492  }
3493 
3494  return false;
3495  }
3496 
3497 };

3651  B[2] = Q[1]*Q[4] - Q[2]*Q[3];
3652  B[3] = Q[0]*Q[5] - Q[2]*Q[2];
3653  B[4] = -Q[0]*Q[4] + Q[1]*Q[2];
3654  B[5] = Q[0]*Q[3] - Q[1]*Q[1];
3655 
3656  dB_dQ(0,0) = 0; dB_dQ(0,1) = 0; dB_dQ(0,2) = 0; dB_dQ(0,3) = Q[5]; dB_dQ(0,4) = -2.0*Q[4]; dB_dQ(0,5) = Q[3];
3657  dB_dQ(1,0) = 0; dB_dQ(1,1) = -Q[5]; dB_dQ(1,2) = Q[4]; dB_dQ(1,3) = 0; dB_dQ(1,4) = Q[2]; dB_dQ(1,5) = -Q[1];
3658  dB_dQ(2,0) = 0; dB_dQ(2,1) = Q[4]; dB_dQ(2,2) = -Q[3]; dB_dQ(2,3) = -Q[2]; dB_dQ(2,4) = Q[1]; dB_dQ(2,5) = 0;
3659  dB_dQ(3,0) = Q[5]; dB_dQ(3,1) = 0; dB_dQ(3,2) = -2.0*Q[2]; dB_dQ(3,3) = 0; dB_dQ(3,4) = 0; dB_dQ(3,5) = Q[0];
3660  dB_dQ(4,0) = -Q[4]; dB_dQ(4,1) = Q[2]; dB_dQ(4,2) = Q[1]; dB_dQ(4,3) = 0; dB_dQ(4,4) = -Q[0]; dB_dQ(4,5) = 0;
3661  dB_dQ(5,0) = Q[3]; dB_dQ(5,1) = -2.0*Q[1]; dB_dQ(5,2) = 0; dB_dQ(5,3) = Q[0]; dB_dQ(5,4) = 0; dB_dQ(5,5) = 0;
3662 
3663  const double detQ = get_J(Q, true);
3664  get_dJ_dF(Q, ddetQ_dQ, true);
3665  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 6; ++i)
3666  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 6; ++j)
3667  dQ_inv_dQ(i,j) = ( dB_dQ(i,j) - B[i] * ddetQ_dQ[j] / detQ ) / detQ;
3668 
3669  }
3670 
3671  const double dd = d * d;
3672  const double dd_n = dd > 0.0 ? pow(dd, n) : 0.0;
3673  const double dd_n_1 = dd > 0.0 ? pow(dd, n-1.0) : 0.0;
3674  const double dd_n_2 = dd > 0.0 ? pow(dd, n-2.0) : 0.0;
3675 
3676  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
3677  {
3678  omega = 0.5 * A/n * dd_n;
3679  }
3680 
3681  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
3682  {
3683  dealii::Vector<double> d_dd_dQ_dot(6);
3684  dd_dQ_dot.Tvmult(d_dd_dQ_dot, d);
3685  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 6; ++m)
3686  d_omega[m] = A * dd_n_1 * d_dd_dQ_dot[m];
3687  }
3688 
3689  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
3690  {
3691  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 9; ++i)
3692  {
3693  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 9; ++j)
3694  d2delta_dd2(i,j) = 2.0 * A * (n - 1.0) * dd_n_2 * d[i] * d[j];
3695  d2delta_dd2(i,i) += A * dd_n_1;
3696  }
3697  d2delta_dd2.mmult(d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot, dd_dQ_dot);
3698  dd_dQ_dot.Tmmult(dd_dQ_dot_d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot, d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot);
3699  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 6; ++i)
3700  {
3701  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 6; ++j)
3702  d2_omega(i,j) = dd_dQ_dot_d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot(i,j);
3703  }
3704 
3705  if(compute_dq)
3706  {
3707  d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot.Tmmult(d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot_T_dd_dQ_inv, dd_dQ_inv);
3708  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 6; ++i)
3709  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 6; ++j)
3710  d2delta_dQ_dot_dQ_inv(i,j) = d2delta_dd2_dd_dQ_dot_T_dd_dQ_inv(i,j) + A * dd_n_1 * d_d2d_dQ_dot_d_Q_inv(i,j);
3711  d2delta_dQ_dot_dQ_inv.mmult(d2delta_dQ_dot_dQ, dQ_inv_dQ);
3712  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 6; ++i)
3713  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 6; ++j)
3714  d2_omega(i,j + 6) = d2delta_dQ_dot_dQ(i,j);
3715  }
3716 
3717  }
3718 
3719  return false;
3720  }
3721 
3722 };
3723

3855  F_t_inv[1][0] = F[3]; F_t_inv[1][1] = F[4]; F_t_inv[1][2] = F[5];

3857  F_t_inv = invert(F_t_inv);

3859  F_inv[3] = F_t_inv[1][0]; F_inv[4] = F_t_inv[1][1]; F_inv[5] = F_t_inv[1][2];

3867  d[4] = 0.5*F_dot[1]*F_inv[3] + 0.5*F_dot[3]*F_inv[1] + F_dot[4]*F_inv[4] + 0.5*F_dot[5]*F_inv[7] + 0.5*F_dot[7]*F_inv[5];

3875  if( (get<1>(requested_quantities)) || (get<2>(requested_quantities)))

3879  dd_dF_dot(2,0) = 0.5*F_inv[2]; dd_dF_dot(2,1) = 0.5*F_inv[5]; dd_dF_dot(2,2) = 0.5*F_inv[0] + 0.5*F_inv[8]; dd_dF_dot(2,3) = 0; dd_dF_dot(2,4) = 0; dd_dF_dot(2,5) = 0.5*F_inv[1]; dd_dF_dot(2,6) = 0; dd_dF_dot(2,7) = 0; dd_dF_dot(2,8) = 0.5*F_inv[2];

3883  dd_dF_dot(6,0) = 0.5*F_inv[6]; dd_dF_dot(6,1) = 0; dd_dF_dot(6,2) = 0; dd_dF_dot(6,3) = 0.5*F_inv[7]; dd_dF_dot(6,4) = 0; dd_dF_dot(6,5) = 0; dd_dF_dot(6,6) = 0.5*F_inv[0] + 0.5*F_inv[8]; dd_dF_dot(6,7) = 0.5*F_inv[3]; dd_dF_dot(6,8) = 0.5*F_inv[6];

3885  dd_dF_dot(8,0) = 0; dd_dF_dot(8,1) = 0; dd_dF_dot(8,2) = 0.5*F_inv[6]; dd_dF_dot(8,3) = 0; dd_dF_dot(8,4) = 0; dd_dF_dot(8,5) = 0.5*F_inv[7]; dd_dF_dot(8,6) = 0.5*F_inv[2]; dd_dF_dot(8,7) = 0.5*F_inv[5]; dd_dF_dot(8,8) = F_inv[8];
3886 
3887  dd_dF_dot.Tvmult(d_dd_dF_dot, d);
3888  }
3889 
3890  const double dd = d * d;
3891  const double sqrt_dd = sqrt(dd);
3892  const double A_0 = A * pow(d_th, 2.0 * (n - 1.0));
3893  const double h = sqrt_dd > d_th ? A / n * pow(dd, n) : A_0 * dd;
3894  const double dh = sqrt_dd > d_th ? A * pow(dd, n - 1.0) : A_0;
3895  const double d2h = sqrt_dd > d_th ? A * (n - 1.0) * pow(dd, n - 2.0) : 0.0;
3896 
3897 // if(sqrt_dd < d_th)
3898 // global_data.set_not_converged_at_local_level();
3899 
3900  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
3901  {
3902  omega = 0.5 * h;
3903  }
3904 
3905  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
3906  {
3907  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 9; ++m)
3908  d_omega[m] = dh * d_dd_dF_dot[m];
3909  }
3910 
3911  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
3912  {
3913  dd_dF_dot.Tmmult(d2delta_dF_dot2, dd_dF_dot);
3914  d2delta_dF_dot2 *= dh;
3915  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 9; ++i)
3916  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 9; ++j)
3917  d2delta_dF_dot2(i,j) += 2.0 * d2h * d_dd_dF_dot[i] * d_dd_dF_dot[j];
3918 
3919  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 9; ++i)
3920  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 9; ++j)
3921  d2_omega(i,j) = d2delta_dF_dot2(i,j);
3922 
3923 
3924  if(compute_dq)
3925  {
3926  dd_dF_inv(0,0) = F_dot[0]; dd_dF_inv(0,1) = 0.5*F_dot[3]; dd_dF_inv(0,2) = 0.5*F_dot[6]; dd_dF_inv(0,3) = 0.5*F_dot[1]; dd_dF_inv(0,4) = 0; dd_dF_inv(0,5) = 0; dd_dF_inv(0,6) = 0.5*F_dot[2]; dd_dF_inv(0,7) = 0; dd_dF_inv(0,8) = 0;
3927  dd_dF_inv(1,0) = 0.5*F_dot[1]; dd_dF_inv(1,1) = 0.5*F_dot[0] + 0.5*F_dot[4]; dd_dF_inv(1,2) = 0.5*F_dot[7]; dd_dF_inv(1,3) = 0; dd_dF_inv(1,4) = 0.5*F_dot[1]; dd_dF_inv(1,5) = 0; dd_dF_inv(1,6) = 0; dd_dF_inv(1,7) = 0.5*F_dot[2]; dd_dF_inv(1,8) = 0;
3928  dd_dF_inv(2,0) = 0.5*F_dot[2]; dd_dF_inv(2,1) = 0.5*F_dot[5]; dd_dF_inv(2,2) = 0.5*F_dot[0] + 0.5*F_dot[8]; dd_dF_inv(2,3) = 0; dd_dF_inv(2,4) = 0; dd_dF_inv(2,5) = 0.5*F_dot[1]; dd_dF_inv(2,6) = 0; dd_dF_inv(2,7) = 0; dd_dF_inv(2,8) = 0.5*F_dot[2];
3929  dd_dF_inv(3,0) = 0.5*F_dot[3]; dd_dF_inv(3,1) = 0; dd_dF_inv(3,2) = 0; dd_dF_inv(3,3) = 0.5*F_dot[0] + 0.5*F_dot[4]; dd_dF_inv(3,4) = 0.5*F_dot[3]; dd_dF_inv(3,5) = 0.5*F_dot[6]; dd_dF_inv(3,6) = 0.5*F_dot[5]; dd_dF_inv(3,7) = 0; dd_dF_inv(3,8) = 0;
3930  dd_dF_inv(4,0) = 0; dd_dF_inv(4,1) = 0.5*F_dot[3]; dd_dF_inv(4,2) = 0; dd_dF_inv(4,3) = 0.5*F_dot[1]; dd_dF_inv(4,4) = F_dot[4]; dd_dF_inv(4,5) = 0.5*F_dot[7]; dd_dF_inv(4,6) = 0; dd_dF_inv(4,7) = 0.5*F_dot[5]; dd_dF_inv(4,8) = 0;
3931  dd_dF_inv(5,0) = 0; dd_dF_inv(5,1) = 0; dd_dF_inv(5,2) = 0.5*F_dot[3]; dd_dF_inv(5,3) = 0.5*F_dot[2]; dd_dF_inv(5,4) = 0.5*F_dot[5]; dd_dF_inv(5,5) = 0.5*F_dot[4] + 0.5*F_dot[8]; dd_dF_inv(5,6) = 0; dd_dF_inv(5,7) = 0; dd_dF_inv(5,8) = 0.5*F_dot[5];
3932  dd_dF_inv(6,0) = 0.5*F_dot[6]; dd_dF_inv(6,1) = 0; dd_dF_inv(6,2) = 0; dd_dF_inv(6,3) = 0.5*F_dot[7]; dd_dF_inv(6,4) = 0; dd_dF_inv(6,5) = 0; dd_dF_inv(6,6) = 0.5*F_dot[0] + 0.5*F_dot[8]; dd_dF_inv(6,7) = 0.5*F_dot[3]; dd_dF_inv(6,8) = 0.5*F_dot[6];
3933  dd_dF_inv(7,0) = 0; dd_dF_inv(7,1) = 0.5*F_dot[6]; dd_dF_inv(7,2) = 0; dd_dF_inv(7,3) = 0; dd_dF_inv(7,4) = 0.5*F_dot[7]; dd_dF_inv(7,5) = 0; dd_dF_inv(7,6) = 0.5*F_dot[1]; dd_dF_inv(7,7) = 0.5*F_dot[4] + 0.5*F_dot[8]; dd_dF_inv(7,8) = 0.5*F_dot[7];
3934  dd_dF_inv(8,0) = 0; dd_dF_inv(8,1) = 0; dd_dF_inv(8,2) = 0.5*F_dot[6]; dd_dF_inv(8,3) = 0; dd_dF_inv(8,4) = 0; dd_dF_inv(8,5) = 0.5*F_dot[7]; dd_dF_inv(8,6) = 0.5*F_dot[2]; dd_dF_inv(8,7) = 0.5*F_dot[5]; dd_dF_inv(8,8) = F_dot[8];

4016  dF_inv_dF(7,7) = -F[0]*F[0]*F[4]*F[8] + F[0]*F[1]*F[3]*F[8] + F[0]*F[2]*F[4]*F[6] - F[1]*F[2]*F[3]*F[6];
4017  dF_inv_dF(7,8) = F[0]*F[0]*F[4]*F[7] - F[0]*F[1]*F[3]*F[7] - F[0]*F[1]*F[4]*F[6] + F[1]*F[1]*F[3]*F[6];
4018  dF_inv_dF(8,0) = -F[1]*F[3]*F[5]*F[7] + F[1]*F[4]*F[5]*F[6] + F[2]*F[3]*F[4]*F[7] - F[2]*F[4]*F[4]*F[6];
4019  dF_inv_dF(8,1) = F[0]*F[3]*F[5]*F[7] - F[0]*F[4]*F[5]*F[6] - F[2]*F[3]*F[3]*F[7] + F[2]*F[3]*F[4]*F[6];
4020  dF_inv_dF(8,2) = -F[0]*F[3]*F[4]*F[7] + F[0]*F[4]*F[4]*F[6] + F[1]*F[3]*F[3]*F[7] - F[1]*F[3]*F[4]*F[6];
4021  dF_inv_dF(8,3) = F[0]*F[1]*F[5]*F[7] - F[0]*F[2]*F[4]*F[7] - F[1]*F[1]*F[5]*F[6] + F[1]*F[2]*F[4]*F[6];
4022  dF_inv_dF(8,4) = -F[0]*F[0]*F[5]*F[7] + F[0]*F[1]*F[5]*F[6] + F[0]*F[2]*F[3]*F[7] - F[1]*F[2]*F[3]*F[6];
4023  dF_inv_dF(8,5) = F[0]*F[0]*F[4]*F[7] - F[0]*F[1]*F[3]*F[7] - F[0]*F[1]*F[4]*F[6] + F[1]*F[1]*F[3]*F[6];
4024  dF_inv_dF(8,6) = -F[0]*F[1]*F[4]*F[5] + F[0]*F[2]*F[4]*F[4] + F[1]*F[1]*F[3]*F[5] - F[1]*F[2]*F[3]*F[4];
4025  dF_inv_dF(8,7) = F[0]*F[0]*F[4]*F[5] - F[0]*F[1]*F[3]*F[5] - F[0]*F[2]*F[3]*F[4] + F[1]*F[2]*F[3]*F[3];
4026  dF_inv_dF(8,8) = -F[0]*F[0]*F[4]*F[4] + 2.0*F[0]*F[1]*F[3]*F[4] - F[1]*F[1]*F[3]*F[3];
4027  dF_inv_dF *= 1.0/get_J(F)/get_J(F);
4028 
4029  dd_dF_inv.Tvmult(d_dd_dF_inv, d);
4030  dd_dF_dot.Tmmult(d2delta_dF_dot_dF_inv, dd_dF_inv);
4031  d2delta_dF_dot_dF_inv *= dh;
4032  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 9; ++i)
4033  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 9; ++j)
4034  d2delta_dF_dot_dF_inv(i,j) += 2.0 * d2h * d_dd_dF_dot[i] * d_dd_dF_inv[j] + dh * d_d2d_dF_dot_d_F_inv(i,j);
4035  d2delta_dF_dot_dF_inv.mmult(d2delta_dF_dot_dF, dF_inv_dF);
4036  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 9; ++i)
4037  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 9; ++j)
4038  d2_omega(i,j + 9) = d2delta_dF_dot_dF(i,j);
4039  }
4040 
4041  }
4042 
4043  return false;
4044  }
4045 
4049  double
4050  get_maximum_step( const dealii::Vector<double>& e_omega,
4051  const std::vector<dealii::Vector<double>>& /*e_omega_ref_sets*/,
4052  const dealii::Vector<double>& delta_e_omega,
4053  const dealii::Vector<double>& /*hidden_vars*/,
4054  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/)
4055  const
4056  {
4057 
4058  double factor = 2.0;
4059  static dealii::Vector<double> F(9);
4060  while(true)
4061  {
4062 
4063  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 9; ++m)
4064  F[m] = e_omega[m] + factor * delta_e_omega[m];
4065  if( (get_J(F) > 0.0) )
4066  break;
4067 
4068  factor *= 0.5;
4069  Assert(factor > 0.0, dealii::ExcMessage("Cannot determine a positive scaling of the load step such that the determinant of the deformation gradient and that of Q stays positive!"));
4070  }
4071  return factor;
4072  }
4073 
4074 };

4114 class OmegaVelocityFlux00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
4115 {
4116 
4117 public:
4118 
4134  OmegaVelocityFlux00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
4135  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,

4144 
4148  bool
4149  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
4150  const double /*t*/,
4151  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
4152  double& omega,
4153  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
4154  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
4155  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
4156  const bool compute_dq)
4157  const
4158  {
4159 
4160  (void)compute_dq;
4161  Assert(!compute_dq, dealii::ExcMessage("The alpha-family for temporal discretization is not currently implemented!"));
4162 
4163  // start indices for respective quantities
4164  const unsigned int i_u_dot = 0;
4165  const unsigned int i_v = 3;
4166  const unsigned int i_I = 6;
4167  const unsigned int i_t = 9;
4168  const unsigned int i_c = 12;
4169  const unsigned int i_F = 13;
4170 
4171  dealii::Tensor<1,3> u_dot, v, I, t_;
4172  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F;
4173  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
4174  {
4175  u_dot[i] = values[i_u_dot + i];
4176  v[i] = values[i_v + i];
4177  I[i] = values[i_I + i];
4178  t_[i] = values[i_t + i];
4179  }
4180  const double c = values[i_c];
4181  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
4182  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 3; ++j)
4183  F[i][j] = values[i_F + i * 3 + j];
4184 
4185  dealii::Tensor<1,3> c_F_I = 1.0/c * F * I;
4186  dealii::Tensor<1,3> c_t_F = 1.0/c * transpose(F) * t_;
4187 
4188  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
4189  {
4190  omega = t_ * (v - u_dot - c_F_I);
4191  }
4192 
4193  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
4194  {
4195  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
4196  {
4197  d_omega[i_u_dot + i] = -t_[i];
4198  d_omega[i_v + i] = t_[i];
4199  d_omega[i_I + i] = -c_t_F[i];
4200  d_omega[i_t + i] = (v - u_dot - c_F_I)[i];
4201  }
4202  }
4203 
4204  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
4205  {
4206  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
4207  {
4208  d2_omega[i_u_dot + i][i_t + i] = d2_omega[i_t + i][i_u_dot + i] = -1.0;
4209  d2_omega[i_v + i][i_t + i] = d2_omega[i_t + i][i_v + i] = 1.0;
4210  for(unsigned int j = 0; j < 3; ++j)
4211  d2_omega[i_I + i][i_t + j] = d2_omega[i_t + j][i_I + i] = -1.0 / c * F[j][i];
4212  }
4213  }
4214 
4215  return false;
4216 
4217  }

4425 template<unsigned int spacedim>
4426 class OmegaViscousDissipation02 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
4427 {
4428 
4429 private:
4430 
4434  const double
4435  eta;
4436 
4437 public:
4438 
4456  OmegaViscousDissipation02( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
4457  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
4458  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
4459  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
4460  const double eta,
4461  const unsigned int method,
4462  const double alpha = 0.0)
4463  :
4464  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 9, 0, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaViscousDissipation02"),
4465  eta(eta)
4466  {
4467  }
4468 
4472  bool
4473  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
4474  const double /*t*/,
4475  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
4476  double& omega,
4477  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
4478  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
4479  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
4480  const bool compute_dq)
4481  const
4482  {
4483 
4484  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_ref_v, F, F_inv, C_inv, grad_v, delta;
4485  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4486  {
4487  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4488  {
4489  grad_ref_v[r][S] = values[3 * r + S];
4490  F[r][S] = values[9 + 3 * r + S];
4491  }
4492  }
4493  F_inv = invert(F);
4494  C_inv = F_inv * transpose(F_inv);
4495  grad_v = grad_ref_v * F_inv;
4496  delta[0][0] = delta[1][1] = delta[2][2] = 1.0;
4497  const double J = determinant(F);
4498 
4499  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
4500  {
4501  omega = 0.5 * J * eta * ( trace(grad_v * transpose(grad_v)) + trace(grad_v * grad_v) );
4502  }
4503 
4504  dealii::Tensor<2,3> T;
4505  if(get<1>(requested_quantities) || get<2>(requested_quantities))
4506  {
4507  T = J * eta * (grad_v + transpose(grad_v)) * transpose(F_inv);
4508  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
4509  {
4510  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4511  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4512  d_omega[r * 3 + S] = T[r][S];
4513  }
4514  }
4515 
4516  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
4517  {
4518  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4519  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4520  for(unsigned int p = 0; p < 3; ++p)
4521  for(unsigned int Q = 0; Q < 3; ++Q)
4522  d2_omega(r * 3 + S, p * 3 + Q) = J * eta * (delta[r][p] * C_inv[S][Q] + F_inv[Q][r] * F_inv[S][p]);
4523  if(compute_dq)
4524  {
4525  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv_grad_v, F_inv_grad_v_T;
4526  F_inv_grad_v = F_inv * grad_v;
4527  F_inv_grad_v_T = F_inv * transpose(grad_v);
4528 
4529  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4530  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4531  for(unsigned int p = 0; p < 3; ++p)
4532  for(unsigned int Q = 0; Q < 3; ++Q)
4533  d2_omega(r * 3 + S, p * 3 + Q + 9) = F_inv[Q][p] * T[r][S] - J * eta * ( F_inv_grad_v[S][p] * F_inv[Q][r] + C_inv[Q][S] * grad_v[r][p] + ( F_inv_grad_v[Q][r] + F_inv_grad_v_T[Q][r] ) * F_inv[S][p] );
4534  }
4535  }
4536 
4537  return false;
4538  }
4539 };

4574 {
4575 
4576 public:
4577 
4593  OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
4594  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,

4597  const unsigned int method,
4598  const double alpha = 0.0)
4599  :
4600  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 1, 0, 9, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility00")
4601  {
4602  }
4603 
4607  bool
4608  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
4609  const double /*t*/,
4610  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
4611  double& omega,
4612  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,

4616  const
4617  {
4618 
4619  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_ref_f, F, F_inv, grad_f;
4620 
4621  const double xi_dot = values[0];
4622  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4623  {
4624  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4625  {
4626  grad_ref_f[r][S] = values[1 + 3 * r + S];
4627  F[r][S] = values[1 + 9 + 3 * r + S];
4628  }
4629  }
4630  F_inv = invert(F);
4631  grad_f = grad_ref_f * F_inv;

4633  const double tr_grad_f = trace(grad_f);
4634

4636  {
4637  omega = -J * tr_grad_f * xi_dot;
4638  }
4639 
4640  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
4641  {
4642  d_omega[0] = -J *tr_grad_f;
4643  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4644  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4645  d_omega[1 + r * 3 + R] = -J * F_inv[R][r] * xi_dot;
4646  }
4647 
4648  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
4649  {
4650  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4651  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4652  d2_omega(0, 1 + r * 3 + R) = d2_omega(1 + r * 3 + R, 0) = -J * F_inv[R][r];
4653 
4654  if(compute_dq)
4655  {
4656  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv_grad_f = F_inv * grad_f;
4657  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4658  {
4659  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4660  {
4661  d2_omega(0, 1 + 9 + r * 3 + R) = -J * ( tr_grad_f * F_inv[R][r] - F_inv_grad_f[R][r]);
4662  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
4663  for(unsigned int K = 0; K < 3; ++K)
4664  d2_omega(1 + k * 3 + K, 1 + 9 + r * 3 + R) = -J * xi_dot * ( F_inv[R][r] * F_inv[K][k] - F_inv[K][r] * F_inv[R][k] );
4665  }
4666  }
4667  }
4668  }

4670  return false;
4671  }

4701 template<unsigned int spacedim>
4702 class OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility01 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
4703 {
4704 
4705 public:
4706 
4722  OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility01( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
4723  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
4724  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
4725  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
4726  const unsigned int method,
4727  const double alpha = 0.0)
4728  :
4729  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 3, 0, 3, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility01")
4730  {

4732 
4736  bool
4737  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
4738  const double /*t*/,
4739  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
4740  double& omega,
4741  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
4742  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
4743  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
4744  const bool compute_dq)
4745  const
4746  {
4747 
4748  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F, F_inv;
4749  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_xi_dot_ref, f_def, f_ref, grad_xi_dot_def;
4750 
4751  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4752  {
4753  grad_xi_dot_ref[r] = values[r];
4754  f_def[r] = values[3 + r];
4755  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4756  F[r][S] = values[6 + 3 * r + S];
4757  }
4758  F_inv = invert(F);
4759  const double J = determinant(F);
4760 
4761  f_ref = J * F_inv * f_def;
4762  grad_xi_dot_def = J * transpose(F_inv) * grad_xi_dot_ref;
4763 
4764  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
4765  {
4766  omega = f_ref * grad_xi_dot_ref;
4767  }
4768 
4769  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
4770  {
4771  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4772  {
4773  d_omega[r] = f_ref[r];
4774  d_omega[r + 3] = grad_xi_dot_def[r];
4775  }
4776  }
4777 
4778  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
4779  {
4780  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4781  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4782  d2_omega(R, 3 + r) = d2_omega(3 + r, R) = J * F_inv[R][r];
4783 
4784  if(compute_dq)
4785  {
4786  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
4787  {
4788  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4789  {
4790  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4791  {
4792  d2_omega(k, 6 + 3 * r + R) = F_inv[R][r] * f_ref[k] - F_inv[k][r] * f_ref[R];
4793  d2_omega(k + 3, 6 + 3 * r + R) = F_inv[R][r] * grad_xi_dot_def[k] - F_inv[R][k] * grad_xi_dot_def[r];
4794  }
4795  }
4796  }
4797  }
4798  }
4799 
4800  return false;
4801  }
4802 };

4829 template<unsigned int spacedim>
4830 class OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility02 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
4831 {
4832 private:
4833 
4837  const bool
4838  flip_normal;
4839 
4840 public:
4841 
4859  OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility02( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_omega,
4860  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
4861  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
4862  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
4863  const bool flip_normal,
4864  const unsigned int method,
4865  const double alpha = 0.0)
4866  :
4867  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 1, 0, 3, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility02"),
4868  flip_normal(flip_normal)
4869  {
4870  }
4871 
4875  bool
4876  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
4877  const double /*t*/,
4878  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
4879  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
4880  double& sigma,
4881  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
4882  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
4883  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
4884  const bool compute_dq)
4885  const
4886  {
4887 
4888  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F, F_inv;
4889 
4890  const double xi_dot = values[0];
4891  dealii::Tensor<1,3> f;
4892  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4893  {
4894  f[r] = values[1 + r];
4895  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
4896  F[r][S] = values[4 + 3 * r + S];
4897  }
4898  F_inv = invert(F);
4899  const double J = determinant(F);
4900 
4901  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> n__, n_;
4902  n__[0] = n[0];
4903  n__[1] = spacedim < 2 ? 0.0 : n[1];
4904  n__[2] = spacedim < 3 ? 0.0 : n[2];
4905  n_ = flip_normal ? -J * transpose(F_inv) * n__ : J * transpose(F_inv) * n__;
4906 
4907  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
4908  {
4909  sigma = xi_dot * f * n_;
4910  }
4911 
4912  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
4913  {
4914  d_sigma[0] = f * n_;
4915  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4916  d_sigma[1 + r] = xi_dot * n_[r];
4917  }
4918 
4919  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
4920  {
4921 
4922  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4923  d2_sigma(0, 1 + r) = d2_sigma(1 + r, 0) = n_[r];
4924 
4925  if(compute_dq)
4926  {
4927  dealii::Tensor<3,3> dn_dF;
4928  dealii::Tensor<2,3> f_dn_dF;
4929  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
4930  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4931  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4932  dn_dF[m][r][R] = F_inv[R][r] * n_[m] - F_inv[R][m] * n_[r];
4933  f_dn_dF = f * dn_dF;
4934  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
4935  {
4936  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
4937  {
4938  d2_sigma(0, 4 + r * 3 + R) = f_dn_dF[r][R];
4939  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
4940  d2_sigma(1 + k, 4 + r * 3 + R) = xi_dot * dn_dF[k][r][R];
4941  }
4942  }
4943  }
4944  }
4945 
4946  return false;
4947  }

4981 template<unsigned int spacedim>
4982 class OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility03 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
4983 {
4984 
4985 public:
4986 
5002  OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility03( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_omega,
5003  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
5004  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
5005  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
5006  const unsigned int method,
5007  const double alpha = 0.0)
5008  :
5009  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 1, 0, 9, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaLagrangeIncompressibility03")
5010  {
5011  }
5012 
5016  bool
5017  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
5018  const double /*t*/,
5019  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
5020  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& /*n*/,
5021  double& sigma,
5022  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
5023  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
5024  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
5025  const bool compute_dq)
5026  const
5027  {
5028 
5029  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_ref_f, F, F_inv, grad_f;
5030 
5031  const double xi_dot = values[0];
5032  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5033  {
5034  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
5035  {
5036  grad_ref_f[r][S] = values[1 + 3 * r + S];
5037  F[r][S] = values[1 + 9 + 3 * r + S];
5038  }
5039  }
5040  F_inv = invert(F);
5041  grad_f = grad_ref_f * F_inv;
5042  const double J = determinant(F);
5043  const double tr_grad_f = trace(grad_f);
5044 
5045  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
5046  {
5047  sigma = -J * tr_grad_f * xi_dot;
5048  }
5049 
5050  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
5051  {
5052  d_sigma[0] = -J *tr_grad_f;
5053  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5054  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5055  d_sigma[1 + r * 3 + R] = -J * F_inv[R][r] * xi_dot;
5056  }
5057 
5058  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
5059  {
5060  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5061  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5062  d2_sigma(0, 1 + r * 3 + R) = d2_sigma(1 + r * 3 + R, 0) = -J * F_inv[R][r];
5063 
5064  if(compute_dq)
5065  {
5066  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv_grad_f = F_inv * grad_f;
5067  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5068  {
5069  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5070  {
5071  d2_sigma(0, 1 + 9 + r * 3 + R) = -J * ( tr_grad_f * F_inv[R][r] - F_inv_grad_f[R][r]);
5072  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
5073  for(unsigned int K = 0; K < 3; ++K)
5074  d2_sigma(1 + k * 3 + K, 1 + 9 + r * 3 + R) = -J * xi_dot * ( F_inv[R][r] * F_inv[K][k] - F_inv[K][r] * F_inv[R][k] );
5075  }
5076  }
5077  }
5078  }
5079 
5080  return false;
5081  }

5112 template<unsigned int spacedim>
5113 class OmegaFluidIncompressibility00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
5114 {

5162  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,

5164  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
5165  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
5166  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
5167  const bool compute_dq)
5168  const
5169  {
5170 
5171  // start indices for respective quantities
5172  const unsigned int i_v_dot = 0;
5173  const unsigned int i_c_f_dot = 3;
5174  const unsigned int i_u_dot = 4;
5175  const unsigned int i_grad_eta_f = 7;
5176  const unsigned int i_eta_f = 10;
5177  const unsigned int i_F = 11;
5178 
5179  dealii::Tensor<1,3> v_dot;
5180  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5181  v_dot[m] = values[i_v_dot + m];
5182 
5183  const double c_f_dot = values[i_c_f_dot];
5184 
5185  dealii::Tensor<1,3> u_dot;
5186  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5187  u_dot[m] = values[i_u_dot + m];
5188 
5189  const double eta_f = values[i_eta_f];
5190 
5191  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F;
5192  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5193  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
5194  F[m][n] = values[i_F + m * 3 + n];
5195  const double J = determinant(F);
5196  const double c_f = J / V_m_f;
5197 
5198  dealii::Tensor<1,3> grad_eta_c_f, grad_eta_f;
5199  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5200  {
5201  grad_eta_c_f[m] = c_f * values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
5202  grad_eta_f[m] = values[i_grad_eta_f + m];
5203  }
5204 
5205  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv;
5206  dealii::Tensor<1,3> F_inv_delta_v_dot, grad_eta_f_F_inv, grad_eta_c_f_F_inv, delta_v_dot;
5207  F_inv = invert(F);
5208  delta_v_dot = v_dot - u_dot;
5209  F_inv_delta_v_dot = F_inv * delta_v_dot;
5210  grad_eta_f_F_inv = transpose(F_inv) * grad_eta_f;
5211  grad_eta_c_f_F_inv = transpose(F_inv) * grad_eta_c_f;
5212 
5213  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
5214  {
5215  omega = F_inv_delta_v_dot * grad_eta_c_f - eta_f * c_f_dot;
5216  }
5217 
5218  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
5219  {
5220  d_omega[i_c_f_dot] = -eta_f;
5221  d_omega[i_eta_f] = -c_f_dot;
5222  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5223  {
5224  d_omega[i_v_dot + m] = grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[m];
5225  d_omega[i_u_dot + m] = -grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[m];
5226  d_omega[i_grad_eta_f + m] = F_inv_delta_v_dot[m] * c_f;
5227  }
5228  }
5229 
5230  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
5231  {
5232 
5233  d2_omega[i_c_f_dot][i_eta_f] = d2_omega[i_eta_f][i_c_f_dot] = -1.0;
5234 
5235  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5236  {
5237  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
5238  {
5239  d2_omega(i_v_dot + m, i_grad_eta_f + n) = d2_omega(i_grad_eta_f + n, i_v_dot + m) = F_inv[n][m] * c_f;
5240  d2_omega(i_u_dot + m, i_grad_eta_f + n) = d2_omega(i_grad_eta_f + n, i_u_dot + m) = -F_inv[n][m] * c_f;
5241  }
5242  }
5243 
5244 
5245  if(compute_dq)
5246  {
5247  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5248  {
5249  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
5250  {
5251  for(unsigned int l = 0; l < 3; ++l)
5252  {
5253  d2_omega(i_v_dot + m, i_F + 3 * k + l) = -grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[k] * F_inv[l][m] + grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[m] * F_inv[l][k];
5254  d2_omega(i_u_dot + m, i_F + 3 * k + l) = grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[k] * F_inv[l][m] - grad_eta_c_f_F_inv[m] * F_inv[l][k];
5255  d2_omega(i_grad_eta_f + m, i_F + 3 * k + l) = -F_inv_delta_v_dot[l] * F_inv[m][k] * c_f + F_inv_delta_v_dot[m] * c_f * F_inv[l][k];
5256  }
5257  }
5258 
5259  }
5260 
5261  }
5262 
5263  }
5264  return false;
5265 
5266  }

5370 
5371  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_v_dot;
5372  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)

5375

5377 
5378  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_u_dot;
5379  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5380  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)

5382 
5383  const double eta_f = values[i_eta_f];
5384

5386  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5387  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
5388  F[m][n] = values[i_F + m * 3 + n];
5389  const double J = determinant(F);
5390  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv;
5391  F_inv = invert(F);
5392 
5393  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_v_dot_u_dot = grad_v_dot - grad_u_dot;
5394

5441  }

5546  const
5547  {
5548 
5549  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F, F_inv;
5550 
5551  const double eta_f = values[6];
5552 
5553  dealii::Tensor<1,3> v_dot, u_dot, v_dot_u_dot;
5554  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5555  {
5556  v_dot[r] = values[r];
5557  u_dot[r] = values[3 + r];
5558  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
5559  F[r][S] = values[7 + 3 * r + S];
5560  }
5561  F_inv = invert(F);
5562  const double J = determinant(F);
5563  v_dot_u_dot = v_dot - u_dot;
5564 
5565  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> n__, n_;
5566  n__[0] = n[0];
5567  n__[1] = spacedim < 2 ? 0.0 : n[1];
5568  n__[2] = spacedim < 3 ? 0.0 : n[2];
5569  n_ = flip_normal ? -J * transpose(F_inv) * n__ : J * transpose(F_inv) * n__;
5570 
5571  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
5572  {
5573  sigma = eta_f * v_dot_u_dot * n_ / V_m_f;
5574  }
5575 
5576  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
5577  {
5578  d_sigma[6] = v_dot_u_dot * n_ / V_m_f;
5579  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5580  {
5581  d_sigma[r] = eta_f * n_[r] / V_m_f;
5582  d_sigma[r + 3] = -eta_f * n_[r] / V_m_f;
5583  }
5584  }
5585 
5586  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
5587  {
5588 
5589  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5590  {
5591  d2_sigma(6, r) = d2_sigma(r, 6) = n_[r] / V_m_f;
5592  d2_sigma(6, r + 3) = d2_sigma(r + 3, 6) = -n_[r] / V_m_f;
5593  }
5594 
5595  if(compute_dq)
5596  {
5597  dealii::Tensor<3,3> dn_dF;
5598  dealii::Tensor<2,3> v_dot_u_dot_dn_dF;
5599  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5600  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5601  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5602  dn_dF[m][r][R] = F_inv[R][r] * n_[m] - F_inv[R][m] * n_[r];
5603  v_dot_u_dot_dn_dF = v_dot_u_dot * dn_dF;
5604  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5605  {
5606  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5607  {
5608  d2_sigma(6, 7 + r * 3 + R) = v_dot_u_dot_dn_dF[r][R] / V_m_f;
5609  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
5610  {
5611  d2_sigma(k, 7 + r * 3 + R) = eta_f * dn_dF[k][r][R] / V_m_f;
5612  d2_sigma(k + 3, 7 + r * 3 + R) = -eta_f * dn_dF[k][r][R] / V_m_f;
5613  }
5614  }
5615  }
5616  }
5617  }
5618 
5619  return false;
5620  }
5621 };

5700

5707  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
5708  double& omega,
5709  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
5710  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
5711  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
5712  const bool compute_dq)
5713  const
5714  {
5715 
5716  // start indices for respective quantities
5717  const unsigned int i_grad_v_dot = 0;
5718  const unsigned int i_grad_u_dot = 9;
5719  const unsigned int i_eta_f = 18;
5720  const unsigned int i_F = 19;
5721 
5722  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_v_dot;
5723  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5724  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5725  grad_v_dot[r][R] = values[i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R];
5726 
5727  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_u_dot;
5728  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5729  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5730  grad_u_dot[r][R] = values[i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R];
5731

5733

5735  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
5736  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
5737  F[m][n] = values[i_F + m * 3 + n];
5738  const double J = determinant(F);
5739  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv;
5740  F_inv = invert(F);
5741

5743

5747  }

5755  {
5756  d_omega[i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R] = -J / V_m_f * F_inv[R][r] * eta_f;
5757  d_omega[i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R] = J / V_m_f * F_inv[R][r] * eta_f;
5758  }
5759  }
5760  }
5761

5763  {
5764  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5765  {
5766  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5767  {
5768  d2_omega(i_eta_f, i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R) = d2_omega(i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R, i_eta_f) = -J / V_m_f * F_inv[R][r];
5769  d2_omega(i_eta_f, i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R) = d2_omega(i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R, i_eta_f) = J / V_m_f * F_inv[R][r];
5770  }
5771  }
5772 
5773 
5774  if(compute_dq)
5775  {
5776  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
5777  {
5778  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
5779  {
5780  for(unsigned int s = 0; s < 3; ++s)
5781  {
5782  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
5783  {
5784  d2_omega(i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R, i_F + 3 * s + S) = -J/V_m_f * (F_inv[S][s] * F_inv[R][r] - F_inv[S][r] * F_inv[R][s] ) * eta_f;
5785  d2_omega(i_grad_u_dot + 3 * r + R, i_F + 3 * s + S) = J/V_m_f * (F_inv[S][s] * F_inv[R][r] - F_inv[S][r] * F_inv[R][s] ) * eta_f;
5786  }
5787  }
5788  d2_omega(i_eta_f, i_F + 3 * r + R) = - J/V_m_f * (trace(F_inv * (grad_v_dot_u_dot)) * F_inv[R][r] - (F_inv * (grad_v_dot_u_dot * F_inv))[R][r] );
5789  }
5790  }
5791  }
5792 
5793  }
5794  return false;
5795 
5796  }
