6143 template<unsigned int spacedim>
6144 class OmegaFluidNormalCondition00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
6145 {
6146 
6147 public:
6148 
6164  OmegaFluidNormalCondition00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_omega,
6165  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
6166  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
6167  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
6168  const unsigned int method,
6169  const double alpha = 0.0)
6170  :
6171  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 10, 0, 1, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaFluidNormalCondition00")
6172  {
6173  }
6174 
6178  bool
6179  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
6180  const double /*t*/,
6181  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
6182  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
6183  double& sigma,
6184  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
6185  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
6186  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
6187  const bool compute_dq)
6188  const
6189  {
6190 
6191 
6192  // start indices for respective quantities
6193  const unsigned int i_grad_v_dot = 0;
6194  const unsigned int i_xi_dot = 9;
6195  const unsigned int i_eta = 10;
6196  const unsigned int i_F = 11;
6197 
6198  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_v_dot_ref, grad_v_dot, d;
6199  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6200  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6201  grad_v_dot_ref[r][R] = values[i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R];
6202 
6203  const double xi_dot = values[i_xi_dot];
6204 
6205  const double eta = values[i_eta];
6206 
6207  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F;
6208  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6209  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
6210  F[m][n] = values[i_F + m * 3 + n];
6211  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv;
6212  F_inv = invert(F);
6213 
6214  grad_v_dot = grad_v_dot_ref * F_inv;
6215 
6216  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> n__, n_tilde, F_inv_n_tilde;
6217  n__[0] = n[0];
6218  n__[1] = spacedim < 2 ? 0.0 : n[1];
6219  n__[2] = spacedim < 3 ? 0.0 : n[2];
6220  n_tilde = transpose(F_inv) * n__;
6221 
6222  F_inv_n_tilde = F_inv * n_tilde;
6223 
6224  d = 2.0 * symmetrize(grad_v_dot);
6225 
6226  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6227  d[m][m] += xi_dot;
6228 
6229  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
6230  {
6231  sigma = eta * (n_tilde * d) * n_tilde;
6232  }
6233 
6234  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
6235  {
6236  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6237  for(unsigned int J = 0; J < 3; ++J)
6238  d_sigma[i_grad_v_dot + 3 * i + J] = 2.0 * eta * n_tilde[i] * F_inv_n_tilde[J];
6239  d_sigma[i_xi_dot] = eta * (n_tilde * n_tilde);
6240  d_sigma[i_eta] = (n_tilde * d) * n_tilde;
6241  }
6242 
6243  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
6244  {
6245 
6246  d2_sigma(i_xi_dot, i_eta) = d2_sigma(i_eta, i_xi_dot) = n_tilde * n_tilde;
6247  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6248  for(unsigned int J = 0; J < 3; ++J)
6249  d2_sigma(i_eta, i_grad_v_dot + 3 * i + J) = d2_sigma(i_grad_v_dot + 3 * i + J, i_eta) = 2.0 * n_tilde[i] * F_inv_n_tilde[J];
6250 
6251  if(compute_dq)
6252  {
6253  dealii::Tensor<3,3> dn_tilde_dF, F_inv_dn_tilde_dF;
6254  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
6255  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6256  for(unsigned int J = 0; J < 3; ++J)
6257  dn_tilde_dF[k][i][J] = -n_tilde[i] * F_inv[J][k];
6258  F_inv_dn_tilde_dF = F_inv * dn_tilde_dF;
6259  dealii::Tensor<2,3> n_tilde_dn_tilde_dF = n_tilde * dn_tilde_dF;
6260 
6261  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6262  for(unsigned int J = 0; J < 3; ++J)
6263  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6264  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6265  d2_sigma(i_grad_v_dot + 3 * i + J, i_F + 3 * r + R) = 2.0 * eta * ( dn_tilde_dF[i][r][R] * F_inv_n_tilde[J] + F_inv_dn_tilde_dF[J][r][R] * n_tilde[i] - n_tilde[i] * F_inv[J][r] * F_inv_n_tilde[R] );
6266  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6267  {
6268  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6269  {
6270  d2_sigma(i_xi_dot, i_F + 3 * r + R) = 2.0 * eta * n_tilde_dn_tilde_dF[r][R];
6271  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
6272  for(unsigned int l = 0; l < 3; ++l)
6273  d2_sigma(i_eta, i_F + 3 * r + R) += 2.0 * ( dn_tilde_dF[l][r][R] * d[k][l] * n_tilde[k] - n_tilde[k] * grad_v_dot[k][r] * F_inv[R][l] * n_tilde[l]);
6274  }
6275  }
6276  }
6277  }
6278 
6279  return false;
6280  }
6281 };

6311 template<unsigned int spacedim>
6312 class OmegaFluidNormalCondition01 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
6313 {
6314 
6315 public:
6316 
6332  OmegaFluidNormalCondition01(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_sigma,
6333  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
6334  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
6335  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
6336  const unsigned int method,
6337  const double alpha = 0.0)
6338  :
6339  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_sigma, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 9, 0, 3, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaFluidNormalCondition01")
6340  {
6341  }
6342 
6346  bool
6347  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
6348  const double /*t*/,
6349  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
6350  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
6351  double& sigma,
6352  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
6353  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
6354  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
6355  const bool compute_dq)
6356  const
6357  {
6358 
6359 
6360  // start indices for respective quantities
6361  const unsigned int i_grad_v_dot = 0;
6362  const unsigned int i_f = 9;
6363  const unsigned int i_F = 12;
6364 
6365  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_v_dot_ref, grad_v_dot, d;
6366  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6367  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6368  grad_v_dot_ref[r][R] = values[i_grad_v_dot + 3 * r + R];
6369 
6370  dealii::Tensor<1,3> f;
6371  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6372  f[r] = values[i_f + r];
6373 
6374  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F;
6375  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6376  for(unsigned int n = 0; n < 3; ++n)
6377  F[m][n] = values[i_F + m * 3 + n];
6378  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv, C_inv;
6379  F_inv = invert(F);
6380  C_inv = F_inv * transpose(F_inv);
6381  const double J = determinant(F);
6382 
6383  grad_v_dot = grad_v_dot_ref * F_inv;
6384 
6385  dealii::Tensor<1,3> N, n_, n_tilde;
6386  N[0] = n[0];
6387  N[1] = spacedim < 2 ? 0.0 : n[1];
6388  N[2] = spacedim < 3 ? 0.0 : n[2];
6389 
6390  const double h = sqrt(N * C_inv * N);
6391  n_tilde = J * N * F_inv;
6392  n_ = n_tilde / h;
6393 
6394  dealii::Tensor<1,3> F_inv_n = F_inv * n_;
6395  const double n_tilde_f = n_tilde * f;
6396 
6397  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
6398  {
6399  sigma = - 2.0 * (n_ * grad_v_dot * n_) * (n_tilde * f);
6400  }
6401 
6402  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
6403  {
6404  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6405  for(unsigned int N = 0; N < 3; ++N)
6406  d_sigma[i_grad_v_dot + 3 * m + N] = -2.0 * n_[m] * F_inv_n[N] * n_tilde_f;
6407  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6408  d_sigma[i_f + i] = -2.0 * (n_ * grad_v_dot * n_) * n_tilde[i];
6409  }
6410 
6411  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
6412  {
6413 
6414  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6415  for(unsigned int N = 0; N < 3; ++N)
6416  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6417  d2_sigma(i_grad_v_dot + 3 * m + N, i_f + i) = d2_sigma(i_f + i, i_grad_v_dot + 3 * m + N) = -2.0 * n_[m] * F_inv_n[N] * n_tilde[i];
6418 
6419  if(compute_dq)
6420  {
6421  dealii::Tensor<2,3> dh_dF;
6422  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6423  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6424  dh_dF[r][R] = -1.0 / J * n_[r] * (N * C_inv)[R];
6425  dealii::Tensor<3,3> dn_dF, F_inv_dn_dF;
6426  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
6427  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6428  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6429  dn_dF[k][r][R] = F_inv[R][r] * n_[k] - F_inv[R][k] * n_[r] - n_[k] / h * dh_dF[r][R];
6430  F_inv_dn_dF = F_inv * dn_dF;
6431  dealii::Tensor<1,3> F_inv_f = F_inv * f;
6432 
6433 // dealii::Tensor<2,3> n_tilde_dn_tilde_dF = n_tilde * dn_tilde_dF;
6434 
6435  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6436  for(unsigned int N = 0; N < 3; ++N)
6437  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6438  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6439  d2_sigma(i_grad_v_dot + 3 * m + N, i_F + 3 * r + R) = -2.0 * dn_dF[m][r][R] * F_inv_n[N] * n_tilde_f
6440  - 2.0 * n_[m] * F_inv_dn_dF[N][r][R] * n_tilde_f
6441  - 2.0 * n_[m] * F_inv_n[N] *(F_inv[R][r] * n_tilde_f - F_inv_f[R] * n_tilde[r])
6442  + 2.0 * n_[m] * ( F_inv[N][r] * F_inv_n[R] * n_tilde_f);
6443  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6444  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6445  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6446  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
6447  for(unsigned int l = 0; l < 3; ++l)
6448  d2_sigma(i_f + i, i_F + 3 * r + R) += -2.0 * dn_dF[k][r][R] * grad_v_dot[k][l] * n_[l] * n_tilde[i]
6449  -2.0 * n_[k] * grad_v_dot[k][l] * dn_dF[l][r][R] * n_tilde[i]
6450  -2.0 * n_[k] * grad_v_dot[k][l] * n_[l] * ( F_inv[R][r] * n_tilde[i] - F_inv[R][i] * n_tilde[r])
6451  +2.0 * n_[k] * grad_v_dot[k][r] * F_inv[R][l] * n_[l] * n_tilde[i];
6452  }
6453  }
6454 
6455  return false;
6456  }
6457 };

6500 template<unsigned int spacedim>
6501 class OmegaLagrangeViscousDissipation00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
6502 {
6503 
6504 public:
6505 
6521  OmegaLagrangeViscousDissipation00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
6522  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
6523  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
6524  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
6525  const unsigned int method,
6526  const double alpha = 0.0)
6527  :
6528  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 9, 0, 9, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaLagrangeViscousDissipation00")
6529  {
6530  }
6531 
6535  bool
6536  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
6537  const double /*t*/,
6538  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
6539  double& omega,
6540  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
6541  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
6542  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
6543  const bool compute_dq)
6544  const
6545  {
6546 
6547  dealii::Tensor<2,3> grad_ref_v, grad_ref_f, F, F_inv, C_inv, grad_v, grad_f, grad_v_sym, grad_f_sym, delta;
6548  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6549  {
6550  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
6551  {
6552  grad_ref_v[r][S] = values[3 * r + S];
6553  grad_ref_f[r][S] = values[9 + 3 * r + S];
6554  F[r][S] = values[18 + 3 * r + S];
6555  }
6556  }
6557  F_inv = invert(F);
6558  C_inv = F_inv * transpose(F_inv);
6559  grad_v = grad_ref_v * F_inv;
6560  grad_v_sym = symmetrize(grad_v);
6561  grad_f = grad_ref_f * F_inv;
6562  grad_f_sym = symmetrize(grad_f);
6563  delta[0][0] = delta[1][1] = delta[2][2] = 1.0;
6564  const double J = determinant(F);
6565 
6566  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
6567  {
6568  omega = 2.0 * J * trace( grad_f * symmetrize(grad_v) );
6569  }
6570 
6571  dealii::Tensor<2,3> T_f, T_v;
6572  if(get<1>(requested_quantities) || get<2>(requested_quantities))
6573  {
6574  T_f = 2.0 * J * grad_f_sym * transpose(F_inv);
6575  T_v = 2.0 * J * grad_v_sym * transpose(F_inv);
6576  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
6577  {
6578  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6579  {
6580  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
6581  d_omega[r * 3 + S] = T_f[r][S];
6582  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
6583  d_omega[9 + r * 3 + S] = T_v[r][S];
6584  }
6585  }
6586  }
6587 
6588  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
6589  {
6590  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6591  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
6592  for(unsigned int p = 0; p < 3; ++p)
6593  for(unsigned int Q = 0; Q < 3; ++Q)
6594  d2_omega(r * 3 + S, 9 + p * 3 + Q) = d2_omega(9 + p * 3 + Q, r * 3 + S) = J * (delta[r][p] * C_inv[S][Q] + F_inv[Q][r] * F_inv[S][p]);
6595  if(compute_dq)
6596  {
6597  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F_inv_grad_v, F_inv_grad_v_T, F_inv_grad_f, F_inv_grad_f_T;
6598  F_inv_grad_v = F_inv * grad_v;
6599  F_inv_grad_v_T = F_inv * transpose(grad_v);
6600  F_inv_grad_f = F_inv * grad_f;
6601  F_inv_grad_f_T = F_inv * transpose(grad_f);
6602 
6603  for(unsigned int i = 0; i < 3; ++i)
6604  {
6605  for(unsigned int I = 0; I < 3; ++I)
6606  {
6607  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6608  {
6609  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6610  {
6611  d2_omega(i * 3 + I, r * 3 + R + 18) = F_inv[R][r] * T_f[i][I] - J * ( F_inv_grad_f[I][r] * F_inv[R][i] + C_inv[R][I] * grad_f[i][r] + ( F_inv_grad_f[R][i] + F_inv_grad_f_T[R][i] ) * F_inv[I][r] );
6612  d2_omega(9 + i * 3 + I, r * 3 + R + 18) = F_inv[R][r] * T_v[i][I] - J * ( F_inv_grad_v[I][r] * F_inv[R][i] + C_inv[R][I] * grad_v[i][r] + ( F_inv_grad_v[R][i] + F_inv_grad_v_T[R][i] ) * F_inv[I][r] );
6613  }
6614  }
6615  }
6616  }
6617  }
6618  }
6619 
6620  return false;
6621  }
6622 };

6657 template<unsigned int spacedim>
6658 class OmegaZeroTangentialFlux00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
6659 {
6660 private:
6661 
6665  const bool
6666  flip_normal;
6667 
6668 public:
6669 
6687  OmegaZeroTangentialFlux00( const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_omega,
6688  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
6689  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
6690  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
6691  const bool flip_normal,
6692  const unsigned int method,
6693  const double alpha = 0.0)
6694  :
6695  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 6, 0, 3, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaZeroTangentialFlux00"),
6696  flip_normal(flip_normal)
6697  {
6698  }
6699 
6703  bool
6704  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
6705  const double /*t*/,
6706  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
6707  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
6708  double& sigma,
6709  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
6710  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
6711  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
6712  const bool compute_dq)
6713  const
6714  {
6715 
6716  dealii::Tensor<1,3> u_dot, v_dot, u_dot_v_dot, t;
6717  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F, F_inv;
6718 
6719 
6720  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6721  {
6722  u_dot[r] = values[r];
6723  v_dot[r] = values[3 + r];
6724  t[r] = values[6 + r];
6725  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
6726  F[r][S] = values[9 + 3 * r + S];
6727  }
6728  F_inv = invert(F);
6729  u_dot_v_dot = u_dot - v_dot;
6730  const double J = determinant(F);
6731 
6732  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> n__, n_;
6733  n__[0] = n[0];
6734  n__[1] = spacedim < 2 ? 0.0 : n[1];
6735  n__[2] = spacedim < 3 ? 0.0 : n[2];
6736  n_ = flip_normal ? -J * transpose(F_inv) * n__ : J * transpose(F_inv) * n__;
6737 
6738  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
6739  {
6740  sigma = t * cross_product_3d(u_dot_v_dot, n_) + 0.5 * (t * n_) * (t * n_);
6741  }
6742 
6743  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
6744  {
6745  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6746  {
6747  d_sigma[r] = cross_product_3d(n_, t)[r];
6748  d_sigma[3 + r] = -cross_product_3d(n_, t)[r];
6749  d_sigma[6 + r] = cross_product_3d(u_dot_v_dot, n_)[r] + (t * n_) * n_[r];
6750  }
6751  }
6752 
6753  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
6754  {
6755  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 0) = d2_sigma(0, 6 + 0) = 0.0;
6756  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 0) = d2_sigma(0, 6 + 1) = -n_[2];
6757  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 0) = d2_sigma(0, 6 + 2) = n_[1];
6758  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 1) = d2_sigma(1, 6 + 0) = n_[2];
6759  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 1) = d2_sigma(1, 6 + 1) = 0.0;
6760  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 1) = d2_sigma(1, 6 + 2) = -n_[0];
6761  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 2) = d2_sigma(2, 6 + 0) = -n_[1];
6762  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 2) = d2_sigma(2, 6 + 1) = n_[0];
6763  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 2) = d2_sigma(2, 6 + 2) = 0.0;
6764 
6765  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 6 + 0) = 0.0;
6766  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 6 + 1) = n_[2];
6767  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 3) = d2_sigma(3, 6 + 2) = -n_[1];
6768  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 4) = d2_sigma(4, 6 + 0) = -n_[2];
6769  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 4) = d2_sigma(4, 6 + 1) = 0.0;
6770  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 4) = d2_sigma(4, 6 + 2) = n_[0];
6771  d2_sigma(6 + 0, 5) = d2_sigma(5, 6 + 0) = n_[1];
6772  d2_sigma(6 + 1, 5) = d2_sigma(5, 6 + 1) = -n_[0];
6773  d2_sigma(6 + 2, 5) = d2_sigma(5, 6 + 2) = 0.0;
6774 
6775  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6776  for(unsigned int l = 0; l < 3; ++l)
6777  d2_sigma(6 + m, 6 + l) = n_[m] * n_[l];
6778 
6779  if(compute_dq)
6780  {
6781  dealii::Tensor<3,3> dn_dF;
6782  dealii::Tensor<2,3> t_dn_dF;
6783  const double t_n = t * n_;
6784  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6785  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6786  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6787  dn_dF[m][r][R] = F_inv[R][r] * n_[m] - F_inv[R][m] * n_[r];
6788  t_dn_dF = t * dn_dF;
6789  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6790  {
6791  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6792  {
6793  d2_sigma(0, 9 + 3 * r + R) = dn_dF[1][r][R] * t[2] - dn_dF[2][r][R] * t[1];
6794  d2_sigma(1, 9 + 3 * r + R) = dn_dF[2][r][R] * t[0] - dn_dF[0][r][R] * t[2];
6795  d2_sigma(2, 9 + 3 * r + R) = dn_dF[0][r][R] * t[1] - dn_dF[1][r][R] * t[0];
6796  d2_sigma(3, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[1][r][R] * t[2] + dn_dF[2][r][R] * t[1];
6797  d2_sigma(4, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[2][r][R] * t[0] + dn_dF[0][r][R] * t[2];
6798  d2_sigma(5, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[0][r][R] * t[1] + dn_dF[1][r][R] * t[0];
6799  d2_sigma(6, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[1][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[2] + dn_dF[2][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[1] + t_dn_dF[r][R] * n_[0] + t_n * dn_dF[0][r][R];
6800  d2_sigma(7, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[2][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[0] + dn_dF[0][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[2] + t_dn_dF[r][R] * n_[1] + t_n * dn_dF[1][r][R];
6801  d2_sigma(8, 9 + 3 * r + R) = -dn_dF[0][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[1] + dn_dF[1][r][R] * u_dot_v_dot[0] + t_dn_dF[r][R] * n_[2] + t_n * dn_dF[2][r][R];
6802  }
6803  }
6804  }
6805  }
6806 
6807  return false;
6808  }
6809 };

6900  dealii::Tensor<1,3> u_dot, v_dot, u_dot_v_dot;
6901  dealii::Tensor<2,3> F, F_inv;
6902 
6903  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6904  {
6905  u_dot[r] = values[r];
6906  v_dot[r] = values[3 + r];
6907 
6908  for(unsigned int S = 0; S < 3; ++S)
6909  F[r][S] = values[7 + 3 * r + S];
6910  }
6911  const double t = values[6];
6912 
6913  F_inv = invert(F);
6914  u_dot_v_dot = u_dot - v_dot;
6915  const double J = determinant(F);
6916 
6917  dealii::Tensor<1, 3> n__, n_;
6918  n__[0] = n[0];
6919  n__[1] = spacedim < 2 ? 0.0 : n[1];
6920  n__[2] = spacedim < 3 ? 0.0 : n[2];
6921  n_ = flip_normal ? -J * transpose(F_inv) * n__ : J * transpose(F_inv) * n__;
6922 
6923  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
6924  {
6925  sigma = t * u_dot_v_dot * n_;
6926  }
6927 
6928  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
6929  {
6930  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6931  {
6932  d_sigma[r] = t * n_[r];
6933  d_sigma[3 + r] = -t * n_[r];
6934  }
6935  d_sigma[6] = u_dot_v_dot * n_;
6936  }
6937 
6938  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
6939  {
6940 
6941  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6942  {
6943  d2_sigma(r,6) = d2_sigma(6,r) = n_[r];
6944  d2_sigma(3 + r,6) = d2_sigma(6,r + 3) = -n_[r];
6945  }
6946 
6947  if(compute_dq)
6948  {
6949  dealii::Tensor<3,3> dn_dF;
6950  dealii::Tensor<2,3> u_dot_v_dot_dn_dF;
6951  for(unsigned int m = 0; m < 3; ++m)
6952  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6953  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6954  dn_dF[m][r][R] = F_inv[R][r] * n_[m] - F_inv[R][m] * n_[r];
6955  u_dot_v_dot_dn_dF = u_dot_v_dot * dn_dF;
6956  for(unsigned int r = 0; r < 3; ++r)
6957  {
6958  for(unsigned int R = 0; R < 3; ++R)
6959  {
6960  for(unsigned int k = 0; k < 3; ++k)
6961  {
6962  d2_sigma(k, 7 + r * 3 + R) = t * dn_dF[k][r][R];
6963  d2_sigma(3 + k, 7 + r * 3 + R) = -t * dn_dF[k][r][R];
6964  }
6965  d2_sigma(6, 7 + r * 3 + R) = u_dot_v_dot_dn_dF[r][R];
6966  }
6967  }
6968  }
6969  }
6970 
6971  return false;
6972  }
6973 };
6974 
6975 
6976 
6990 template<unsigned int spacedim>
6991 class OmegaZeroTangentialFlux2D00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>
6992 {
6993 
6994 public:
6995 
7011  OmegaZeroTangentialFlux2D00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim-1,spacedim>> e_omega,
7012  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
7013  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim-1> quadrature,
7014  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
7015  const unsigned int method,
7016  const double alpha = 0.0)
7017  :
7018  Omega<spacedim-1, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 2, 2, 1, 4, method, alpha, "OmegaZeroTangentialFlux2D00")
7019  {
7020  }
7021 
7025  bool
7026  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
7027  const double /*t*/,
7028  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
7029  const dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim>& n,
7030  double& sigma,
7031  dealii::Vector<double>& d_sigma,
7032  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_sigma,
7033  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
7034  const bool compute_dq)
7035  const
7036  {
7037  (void)compute_dq;
7038  Assert(!compute_dq, dealii::ExcMessage("The alpha-family for temporal discretization is not currently implemented!"));
7039  Assert(spacedim == 2, dealii::ExcMessage("This is currently only implemented in two dimensions!"));
7040 
7041  const double dv_0 = values[0] - values[2];
7042  const double dv_1 = values[1] - values[3];
7043  const double lambda = values[4];
7044 
7045  dealii::Tensor<1, spacedim> n_, t_;
7046  dealii::Tensor<2, spacedim> F;
7047  F[0][0] = values[5];
7048  F[0][1] = values[6];
7049  F[1][0] = values[7];
7050  F[1][1] = values[8];
7051  n_ = transpose(invert(F)) * n;
7052  n_ *= 1.0 / sqrt(n_ * n_);
7053  t_[0] = n_[1];
7054  t_[1] = -n_[0];
7055 
7056  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
7057  {
7058  sigma = lambda * ( t_[0] * dv_0 + t_[1] * dv_1 );
7059  }
7060 
7061  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
7062  {
7063  d_sigma[0] = lambda * t_[0];
7064  d_sigma[1] = lambda * t_[1];
7065  d_sigma[2] = -lambda * t_[0];
7066  d_sigma[3] = -lambda * t_[1];
7067  d_sigma[4] = t_[0] * dv_0 + t_[1] * dv_1;
7068  }
7069 
7070  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
7071  {
7072  d2_sigma(0,4) = d2_sigma(4,0) = t_[0];
7073  d2_sigma(1,4) = d2_sigma(4,1) = t_[1];
7074  d2_sigma(2,4) = d2_sigma(4,2) = -t_[0];
7075  d2_sigma(3,4) = d2_sigma(4,3) = -t_[1];
7076  }
7077 
7078  return false;
7079  }
7080 };

7097 template<unsigned int spacedim>
7098 class OmegaElectricalLoading : public incrementalFE::Omega<0, spacedim>
7099 {
7100 
7101 public:
7102 
7106  double
7107  j_bar = 0.0;
7108 
7112  double
7113  phi = 0.0;
7114 
7118  double
7119  R_el = 0.0;
7120 
7126  unsigned int
7127  loading_type = 0;
7128 
7140  OmegaElectricalLoading( const std::vector<const dealii::GalerkinTools::IndependentField<0, spacedim>*> C,
7141  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
7142  const unsigned int method,
7143  const double alpha)
7144  :
7145  Omega<0, spacedim>(C, global_data, 1, 0, 1, 0, method, alpha, "OmegaElectricalLoading")
7146  {
7147  }
7148 
7149  bool get_values_and_derivatives(const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
7150  const double /*t*/,
7151  double& omega,
7152  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
7153  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
7154  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
7155  const bool /*compute_d2q*/)
7156  const
7157  {
7158  const double j_ap = values[0];
7159  const double phi_ap = values[1];
7160 
7161  if(loading_type == 0)
7162  {
7163  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
7164  omega = -j_bar * phi_ap;
7165 
7166  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
7167  {
7168  d_omega[0] = 0.0;
7169  d_omega[1] = -j_bar;
7170  }
7171 
7172  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
7173  {
7174  d2_omega(0,0) = 0.0;
7175  d2_omega(1,1) = 0.0;
7176  d2_omega(0,1) = d2_omega(1,0) = 0.0;
7177  }
7178  }
7179  else if(loading_type == 1)
7180  {
7181  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
7182  omega = -j_ap * (phi_ap - phi);
7183 
7184  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
7185  {
7186  d_omega[0] = -(phi_ap - phi);
7187  d_omega[1] = -j_ap;
7188  }
7189 
7190  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
7191  {
7192  d2_omega(0,0) = 0.0;
7193  d2_omega(1,1) = 0.0;
7194  d2_omega(0,1) = d2_omega(1,0) = -1.0;
7195  }
7196  }
7197  else if(loading_type == 2)
7198  {
7199  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
7200  omega = -0.5 / R_el * phi_ap * phi_ap;
7201 
7202  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
7203  {
7204  d_omega[0] = 0.0;
7205  d_omega[1] = -1.0 / R_el * phi_ap;
7206  }
7207 
7208  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
7209  {
7210  d2_omega(0,0) = 0.0;
7211  d2_omega(1,1) = -1.0 / R_el;
7212  d2_omega(0,1) = d2_omega(1,0) = 0.0;
7213  }
7214  }
7215  else
7216  {
7217  Assert(false, dealii::ExcMessage("Unknown loading type!"));
7218  }
7219 
7220  return false;
7221  }
7222 };

7240 template<unsigned int spacedim>
7241 class OmegaFluidDissipation00 : public incrementalFE::Omega<spacedim, spacedim>
7242 {
7243 
7244 private:
7245 
7249  const double
7250  D;
7251 
7255  const double
7256  V_m_f;
7257 
7258 
7259 public:
7260 
7280  OmegaFluidDissipation00(const std::vector<dealii::GalerkinTools::DependentField<spacedim,spacedim>> e_omega,
7281  const std::set<dealii::types::material_id> domain_of_integration,
7282  const dealii::Quadrature<spacedim> quadrature,
7283  GlobalDataIncrementalFE<spacedim>& global_data,
7284  const double D,
7285  const double V_m_f,
7286  const unsigned int method,
7287  const double alpha = 0.0)
7288  :
7289  Omega<spacedim, spacedim>(e_omega, domain_of_integration, quadrature, global_data, 0, 3, 0, 9, method, alpha, "OmegaFluidDissipation00"),
7290  D(D),
7291  V_m_f(V_m_f)
7292  {
7293  }
7294 
7298  bool
7299  get_values_and_derivatives( const dealii::Vector<double>& values,
7300  const double /*t*/,
7301  const dealii::Point<spacedim>& /*x*/,
7302  double& omega,
7303  dealii::Vector<double>& d_omega,
7304  dealii::FullMatrix<double>& d2_omega,
7305  const std::tuple<bool, bool, bool> requested_quantities,
7306  const bool compute_dq)
7307  const
7308  {
7309 
7310  const double Idot11 = values[0];
7311  const double Idot21 = values[1];
7312  const double Idot31 = values[2];
7313  const double F11 = values[3];
7314  const double F21 = values[4];
7315  const double F31 = values[5];
7316  const double F41 = values[6];
7317  const double F51 = values[7];
7318  const double F61 = values[8];
7319  const double F71 = values[9];
7320  const double F81 = values[10];
7321  const double F91 = values[11];
7322 
7323  if(get<0>(requested_quantities))
7324  {
7325  omega = (1.0/2.0)*V_m_f*(Idot11*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)) + Idot21*(Idot11*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot21*(((F21)*(F21)) + ((F51)*(F51)) + ((F81)*(F81))) + Idot31*(F21*F31 + F51*F61 + F81*F91)) + Idot31*(Idot11*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91) + Idot21*(F21*F31 + F51*F61 + F81*F91) + Idot31*(((F31)*(F31)) + ((F61)*(F61)) + ((F91)*(F91)))))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7326  }
7327 
7328  if(get<1>(requested_quantities))
7329  {
7330  d_omega(0) = V_m_f*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7331  d_omega(1) = V_m_f*(Idot11*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot21*(((F21)*(F21)) + ((F51)*(F51)) + ((F81)*(F81))) + Idot31*(F21*F31 + F51*F61 + F81*F91))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7332  d_omega(2) = V_m_f*(Idot11*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91) + Idot21*(F21*F31 + F51*F61 + F81*F91) + Idot31*(((F31)*(F31)) + ((F61)*(F61)) + ((F91)*(F91))))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7333  }
7334 
7335  if(get<2>(requested_quantities))
7336  {
7337  d2_omega(0,0) = V_m_f*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71)))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7338  d2_omega(0,1) = V_m_f*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81)/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7339  d2_omega(0,2) = V_m_f*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7340  d2_omega(1,0) = V_m_f*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81)/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7341  d2_omega(1,1) = V_m_f*(((F21)*(F21)) + ((F51)*(F51)) + ((F81)*(F81)))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7342  d2_omega(1,2) = V_m_f*(F21*F31 + F51*F61 + F81*F91)/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7343  d2_omega(2,0) = V_m_f*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7344  d2_omega(2,1) = V_m_f*(F21*F31 + F51*F61 + F81*F91)/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7345  d2_omega(2,2) = V_m_f*(((F31)*(F31)) + ((F61)*(F61)) + ((F91)*(F91)))/(D*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71));
7346  if(compute_dq)
7347  {
7348  d2_omega(0,3) = V_m_f*(-(F51*F91 - F61*F81)*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)) + (2*F11*Idot11 + F21*Idot21 + F31*Idot31)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71))/(D*((F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)));
7349  d2_omega(0,4) = V_m_f*(F11*Idot21*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71) + (F41*F91 - F61*F71)*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)))/(D*((F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)));
7350  d2_omega(0,5) = V_m_f*(F11*Idot31*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71) - (F41*F81 - F51*F71)*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)))/(D*((F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)));

7352  d2_omega(0,7) = V_m_f*(F41*Idot21*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71) - (F11*F91 - F31*F71)*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)))/(D*((F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)));
7353  d2_omega(0,8) = V_m_f*(F41*Idot31*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71) + (F11*F81 - F21*F71)*(Idot11*(((F11)*(F11)) + ((F41)*(F41)) + ((F71)*(F71))) + Idot21*(F11*F21 + F41*F51 + F71*F81) + Idot31*(F11*F31 + F41*F61 + F71*F91)))/(D*((F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)*(F11*F51*F91 - F11*F61*F81 - F21*F41*F91 + F21*F61*F71 + F31*F41*F81 - F31*F51*F71)));
